    "content": "{\\rtf1\\ansi\\ansicpg1252\\uc1\\htmautsp\\deff2{\\fonttbl{\\f0\\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}{\\f2\\fcharset0 Georgia;}{\\f3\\fcharset0 Noto Serif;}}{\\colortbl\\red0\\green0\\blue0;\\red255\\green255\\blue255;}\\loch\\hich\\dbch\\pard\\plain\\ltrpar\\itap0{\\lang1033\\fs30\\f3\\cf0 \\cf0\\qj{\\cf1 \\cf1\\ql{{\\ltrch \"T\\u432?\\u417?ng lai, n\\u7871?u ng\\u432?\\u417?i c\\'f3 th\\u7875? ng\\u7897? \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c huy\\u7873?n c\\u417? c\\u7911?a tr\\u7901?i \\u273?\\u7845?t, n\\'f3i kh\\'f4ng ch\\u7915?ng ta v\\'e0 ng\\u432?\\u417?i v\\u7851?n c\\'f2n c\\u417? h\\u7897?i g\\u7863?p l\\u7841?i. . .\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Gi\\u7885?ng n\\'f3i gi\\'e0 nua v\\u7915?a d\\u7913?t c\\u361?ng l\\'e0 l\\'fac th\\'e2n \\u7843?nh Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917? bi\\u7871?n m\\u7845?t kh\\u7887?i th\\u7871? gian.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Ngay kho\\u7843?nh kh\\u7855?c \\u273?\\'f3, c\\'e1nh c\\u7917?a ti\\'ean gi\\u7899?i phun ra m\\u7897?t c\\u7895? ti\\'ean kh\\'ed n\\u7891?ng \\u273?\\u7853?m, gi\\u7889?ng nh\\u432? thi\\'ean \\u273?\\u7883?a \\u273?ang ch\\'fac ph\\'fac cho nh\\u7919?ng ng\\u432?\\u7901?i \\u7903? l\\u7841?i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nh\\u7919?ng c\\u432?\\u7901?ng gi\\u7843? \\u273?\\u7871?n \\u272?\\u7841?i Th\\u7915?a K\\u7923? \\u273?\\u7873?u c\\u7843?m \\u7913?ng \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c c\\u7895? ti\\'ean kh\\'ed n\\u7891?ng \\u273?\\u7853?m n\\'e0y, to\\'e0n b\\u7897? \\u273?\\u7873?u nhao nhao kinh h\\u7881?, l\\u7853?p t\\u7913?c nh\\u7855?m m\\u7855?t c\\u7843?m ng\\u7897?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch C\\'f2n nh\\u7919?ng ng\\u432?\\u7901?i d\\u432?\\u7899?i \\u272?\\u7841?i Th\\u7915?a K\\u7923?, m\\u7863?c d\\'f9 kh\\'f4ng hi\\u7875?u ti\\'ean kh\\'ed, nh\\u432?ng ai c\\u361?ng bi\\u7871?t \\u273?\\'e2y l\\'e0 \\u273?\\u7841?i c\\u417? duy\\'ean.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n}\r\n}\r\n}"
