    "content": "{\\rtf1\\ansi\\ansicpg1252\\uc1\\htmautsp\\deff2{\\fonttbl{\\f0\\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}{\\f2\\fcharset0 Georgia;}{\\f3\\fcharset0 Noto Serif;}}{\\colortbl\\red0\\green0\\blue0;\\red255\\green255\\blue255;}\\loch\\hich\\dbch\\pard\\plain\\ltrpar\\itap0{\\lang1033\\fs30\\f3\\cf0 \\cf0\\qj{\\cf1 \\cf1\\ql{{\\ltrch Tr\\u432?\\u417?ng H\\'f9ng v\\u7899?i H\\'f9ng \\u272?\\u7841?i H\\u7843?i nghe v\\u7853?y th\\'ec x\\'fac \\u273?\\u7897?ng kh\\'f4ng th\\'f4i, h\\u7853?n kh\\'f4ng th\\u7875? g\\'e0o th\\'e9t cho m\\u7885?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i c\\'f9ng bi\\u7871?t.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \\u272?\\'e1m l\\'e3o gi\\u7843? quan s\\'e1t th\\u7845?y h\\'e0nh \\u273?\\u7897?ng c\\u7911?a b\\u7885?n h\\u7855?n th\\'ec g\\u7853?t \\u273?\\u7847?u t\\'e1n th\\u432?\\u7903?ng, \\u273?\\'e2y m\\u7899?i l\\'e0 t\\u7853?p th\\u7875? c\\'f9ng ti\\u7871?n ch\\u7913?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch B\\u7845?t qu\\'e1, khi \\u273?\\u7871?n n\\u417?i m\\u7885?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i m\\u7899?i bi\\u7871?t, nguy\\'ean lai kh\\'f4ng ph\\u7843?i hai ng\\u432?\\u7901?i kia l\\u432?\\u7901?i bi\\u7871?ng, m\\'e0 do c\\u7887? n\\u417?i \\u273?\\'e2y m\\u7885?c qu\\'e1 nhi\\u7873?u, \\u273?\\u7871?n m\\u7897?t khe h\\u7903? c\\u361?ng kh\\'f4ng c\\'f3, n\\'ean l\\'e0m ch\\u7853?m l\\'e0 \\u273?i\\u7873?u hi\\u7875?n nhi\\'ean.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nh\\u432?ng b\\u7885?n h\\u7855?n l\\u7841?i c\\'f3 r\\u7845?t nhi\\u7873?u ng\\u432?\\u7901?i, hai m\\u432?\\u417?i b\\u7889?n ng\\u432?\\u7901?i t\\u7853?p trung d\\u7885?n c\\u7887? trong ph\\u7841?m vi t\\'e1m m\\u432?\\u417?i b\\u7889?n th\\u432?\\u7899?c, \\u273?\\'e2y tuy\\u7879?t \\u273?\\u7889?i l\\'e0 r\\u7845?t nhanh.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Kh\\'f4ng \\u273?\\u7871?n n\\u7917?a ti\\u7871?ng sau, c\\u7843? l\\u7899?p \\u273?\\u7891?ng lo\\u7841?t r\\u7901?i kh\\u7887?i linh \\u273?i\\u7873?n, ti\\u7871?n \\u273?\\u7871?n t\\'ecm m\\u7897?t g\\u7889?c c\\'e2y ng\\u7891?i ngh\\u7881? ng\\u417?i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch M\\u7843?nh linh \\u273?i\\u7873?n d\\u432?\\u7899?i ch\\'e2n l\\'fac n\\'e0y \\u273?\\'e3 \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c nh\\u7893? s\\u7841?ch c\\u7887?, \\u273?\\u7871?n m\\u7897?t chi\\u7871?c l\\'e1 c\\u361?ng kh\\'f4ng th\\u7845?y.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Th\\u7901?i \\u273?i\\u7875?m c\\u7843? l\\u7899?p \\u273?\\u7883?nh r\\u7901?i \\u273?i, ph\\'eda xa b\\u7895?ng nhi\\'ean truy\\u7873?n \\u273?\\u7871?n ti\\u7871?ng b\\u432?\\u7899?c ch\\'e2n d\\u7891?n d\\u7853?p.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch D\\u7851?n \\u273?\\u7847?u l\\'e0 m\\u7897?t trung ni\\'ean m\\u7863?c y ph\\u7909?c ngo\\u7841?i m\\'f4n, sau l\\u432?ng l\\'e0 b\\u7889?n m\\u432?\\u417?i g\\'e3 s\\u432? huynh ngo\\u7841?i m\\'f4n kh\\'e1c.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch B\\u7885?n h\\u7885? ph\\'e2n bi\\u7879?t th\\'e0nh hai nh\\'f3m, m\\u7897?t nh\\'f3m mang theo m\\u7897?t c\\'e1i t\\'fai th\\u7853?t to, c\\u361?ng kh\\'f4ng bi\\u7871?t b\\'ean trong ch\\u7913?a th\\u7913? g\\'ec.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch C\\'f2n nh\\'f3m kia th\\'ec \\u273?\\u7913?ng m\\u7897?t b\\'ean quan s\\'e1t, th\\'e1i \\u273?\\u7897? d\\u432?\\u7901?ng nh\\u432? r\\u7845?t ung dung t\\u7921? t\\u7841?i, gi\\u7889?ng nh\\u432? \\u273?\\'e3 ki\\u7871?m \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c m\\u7897?t m\\'f3n h\\u7901?i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Long B\\'e1 Thi\\'ean c\\u361?ng kh\\'f4ng c\\'f3 l\\'ean ti\\u7871?ng gi\\u7843?i th\\'edch, v\\'ec \\u273?\\'e2y l\\'e0 l\\u7847?n \\u273?\\u7847?u t\\u7899?i \\u273?\\'e2y l\\'e0m nhi\\u7879?m v\\u7909? n\\'ean c\\'f3 ch\\'fat t\\'f2 m\\'f2.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch D\\u432?\\u7899?i s\\u7921? kh\\'f3 hi\\u7875?u c\\u7911?a c\\u7843? l\\u7899?p, hai m\\u432?\\u417?i v\\u7883? s\\u432? huynh d\\u7851?n \\u273?\\u7847?u m\\u7903? t\\'fai, l\\u7845?y nh\\u7919?ng h\\u7841?t m\\'e0u v\\'e0ng r\\u7843?i xu\\u7889?ng linh \\u273?i\\u7873?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch B\\u7885?n h\\u7885? r\\u7843?i xong m\\u7843?nh linh \\u273?i\\u7873?n n\\'e0y, l\\u7853?p t\\u7913?c ch\\u7841?y sang m\\u7843?nh linh \\u273?i\\u7873?n kh\\'e1c, ch\\u7881? trong ch\\u7899?p m\\u7855?t \\u273?\\'e3 x\\u7917? l\\'fd xong m\\u7897?t khu v\\u7921?c l\\u7899?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Trong \\u273?\\'f3 c\\'f3 m\\u7897?t v\\'e0i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i l\\'e0m h\\u7855?n ch\\'fa \\'fd t\\u7899?i, nh\\u7919?ng ng\\u432?\\u7901?i n\\'e0y ch\\'e2n \\u273?\\u7841?p m\\'e2y tr\\u7855?ng, sau \\u273?\\'f3 thong dong r\\u7843?i h\\u7841?t xu\\u7889?ng, kh\\'e1c h\\u7859?n v\\u7899?i nh\\u7919?ng ng\\u432?\\u7901?i kh\\'e1c.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"B\\u7885?n h\\u7885? \\u273?ang gieo tr\\u7891?ng linh c\\u7889?c?\" Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n th\\u7847?m suy \\u273?o\\'e1n, nh\\u432?ng qu\\u7843? th\\u7853?t h\\u7855?n ngh\\u297? kh\\'f4ng sai.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nh\\u7919?ng h\\u7841?t m\\'e0u v\\'e0ng kia ch\\'ednh l\\'e0 linh c\\u7889?c, kh\\'f4ng \\u273?\\u7871?n m\\u432?\\u7901?i ng\\'e0y sau, b\\u7885?n ch\\'fang s\\u7869? \\u273?\\'e2m ch\\u7891?i n\\u7843?y l\\u7897?c.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nh\\'ecn c\\u7843?nh t\\u432?\\u7907?ng n\\'e0y, Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n v\\'f4 c\\'f9ng ph\\u7845?n kh\\'edch, h\\u7855?n c\\u361?ng mu\\u7889?n \\u273?\\u7841?p m\\'e2y gieo tr\\u7891?ng nh\\u432? th\\u7871?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch B\\u7845?t qu\\'e1, ngay l\\'fac nh\\'f3m ng\\u432?\\u7901?i \\u273?\\u7847?u ti\\'ean v\\u7915?a gieo xong, hai m\\u432?\\u417?i m\\u7845?y s\\u432? huynh \\u273?ang \\u273?\\u7913?ng nh\\'ecn t\\u7915? n\\'e3y t\\u7899?i gi\\u7901? r\\u7889?t cu\\u7897?c \\u273?\\'e3 \\u273?\\u7897?ng th\\u7911?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Ch\\u7881? th\\u7845?y b\\u7885?n h\\u7885? \\u273?\\u7913?ng b\\'ean d\\u432?\\u7899?i thi tri\\u7875?n m\\u7845?y lo\\u7841?i \\u7845?n quy\\u7871?t, mi\\u7879?ng l\\u7849?m b\\u7849?m g\\'ec \\u273?\\'f3, m\\u7897?t h\\u7891?i li\\u7873?n ng\\u432?ng t\\u7909? th\\'e0nh m\\u7897?t \\u273?\\'e1m m\\'e2y \\u273?en.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Sau \\u273?\\'f3 h\\u417?i n\\u432?\\u7899?c ng\\u432?ng t\\u7909? n\\u7863?ng h\\u7841?t li\\u7873?n r\\u417?i xu\\u7889?ng m\\u7863?t \\u273?\\u7845?t, cho t\\u7899?i khi n\\'e0o th\\u7845?y \\u273?\\u7911? th\\'ec ng\\u7915?ng thi tri\\u7875?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n \\u273?\\u7847?u ti\\'ean l\\'e0 h\\'e1 h\\u7889?c m\\u7891?m, sau \\u273?\\'f3 l\\u7863?ng thinh nh\\u432? t\\u7901?, \\u273?\\u7913?ng m\\u7897?t b\\'ean quan s\\'e1t h\\'e0nh \\u273?\\u7897?ng c\\u7911?a nh\\u7919?ng ng\\u432?\\u7901?i kia.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"Ch\\u7859?ng tr\\'e1ch \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c x\\u432?ng l\\'e0 ti\\'ean nh\\'e2n, sao ta l\\u7841?i qu\\'ean m\\u7845?t chuy\\u7879?n n\\'e0y?\" Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n t\\u7921? gi\\u7877?u ch\\'ednh m\\'ecnh.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \\u272?\\'e3 l\\'e0 ti\\'ean nh\\'e2n th\\'ec m\\u7845?y chuy\\u7879?n t\\u432?\\u7899?i n\\u432?\\u7899?c n\\'e0y d\\u7877? nh\\u432? \\u259?n c\\u417?m, ch\\u7881? l\\'e0 do h\\u7855?n kh\\'f4ng bi\\u7871?t m\\'e0 th\\'f4i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch C\\u7843? l\\u7899?p ng\\u7891?i nh\\'ecn m\\u7897?t l\\'fac, linh th\\u7889?ng \\u273?\\u7897?t nhi\\'ean vang l\\'ean \\'e2m thanh th\\'f4ng b\\'e1o, Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n th\\u7845?y v\\u7853?y, thu\\u7853?n tay m\\u7903? ra xem.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"\\u272?inh! Ch\\'fac m\\u7915?ng h\\u7885?c sinh K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n \\u273?\\'e3 ho\\'e0n th\\'e0nh nhi\\u7879?m v\\u7909? \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c giao, \\u273?i\\u7875?m linh tr\\u7883? nh\\u7853?n \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c th\\'e1ng n\\'e0y l\\'e0 3 \\u273?i\\u7875?m!\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nh\\u7919?ng ng\\u432?\\u7901?i kh\\'e1c c\\u361?ng \\u273?\\u7891?ng lo\\u7841?t m\\u7903? linh th\\u7889?ng, th\\u7845?y n\\u7897?i dung th\\'f4ng b\\'e1o l\\u7853?p t\\u7913?c t\\u432?\\u417?i c\\u432?\\u7901?i nh\\u432? hoa.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Ng\\u7891?i ngh\\u7881? m\\u7897?t l\\'fac, c\\u7843? l\\u7899?p quy\\u7871?t \\u273?\\u7883?nh ra v\\u7873?, c\\'f2n h\\u7855?n v\\u7899?i T\\u7917? V\\'e2n v\\'e0 b\\u7889?n ng\\u432?\\u7901?i Long B\\'e1 Thi\\'ean th\\'ec \\u273?i \\u273?\\u7871?n qu\\'e1n v\\u7881?a h\\'e8 ng\\u7891?i \\u259?n u\\u7889?ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Trong l\\'fac n\\'f3i chuy\\u7879?n, Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n c\\u361?ng thu\\u7853?n mi\\u7879?ng h\\u7887?i th\\u259?m, th\\'ec ra ph\\'e1p thu\\u7853?t t\\u7841?o m\\u432?a kia t\\'ean \"Ti\\u7875?u V\\'e2n V\\u361? Quy\\u7871?t\".}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \\u272?\\'e2y l\\'e0 m\\u7897?t lo\\u7841?i ph\\'e1p thu\\u7853?t d\\'f9ng \\u273?\\u7875? t\\u7841?o m\\u432?a, ch\\'ednh l\\'e0 h\\'f4 m\\u432?a g\\u7885?i gi\\'f3 trong truy\\u7873?n thuy\\u7871?t.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nh\\u432?ng khi bi\\u7871?t \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c lo\\u7841?i ti\\'ean thu\\u7853?t n\\'e0y d\\u432?\\u7899?i t\\u7847?ng ba kh\\'f4ng th\\u7875? thi tri\\u7875?n, Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n \\u273?\\'e0nh th\\u7903? d\\'e0i m\\u7897?t h\\u417?i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch C\\u7843? \\u273?\\'e1m n\\'f3i n\\'f3i c\\u432?\\u7901?i c\\u432?\\u7901?i v\\u7899?i nhau, \\u273?\\u7871?n chi\\u7873?u m\\u7899?i ch\\u7883?u tr\\u7903? v\\u7873? ti\\u7875?u vi\\u7879?n ho\\u7863?c nh\\'e0 c\\u7911?a m\\'ecnh.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \\u272?\\u7871?n ng\\'e0y h\\'f4m sau, b\\u7885?n h\\u7855?n l\\u7841?i \\u273?\\u7871?n H\\u7885?c Ph\\u7911? \\u273?\\u7875? h\\u7885?c th\\'eam c\\'e1c lo\\u7841?i tri th\\u7913?c m\\u7899?i, nh\\u7901? \\u273?\\'f3 bi\\u7871?t th\\'eam r\\u7845?t nhi\\u7873?u th\\'f4ng tin b\\u7893? \\'edch.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \\u272?\\u7871?n tr\\u432?a, Long B\\'e1 Thi\\'ean \\u273?\\u7897?t nhi\\'ean \\u273?\\u7913?ng ra gi\\u7919?a l\\u7899?p, tr\\u7847?m l\\u7885?ng l\\'ean ti\\u7871?ng \\u273?\\u7873? ngh\\u7883?:}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"Ta nghe n\\'f3i d\\u432?\\u7899?i Quang Huy Chi Th\\'e0nh c\\'f3 m\\u7897?t ng\\u7885?n n\\'fai t\\'ean Ti\\'ean Duy\\'ean S\\u417?n. Ch\\u7881? c\\u7847?n \\u273?\\u7913?ng t\\u7915? \\u273?\\u7881?nh n\\'fai nh\\u7843?y xu\\u7889?ng m\\'e0 kh\\'f4ng ch\\u7871?t s\\u7869? nh\\u7853?n \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c m\\u7897?t quy\\u7875?n \\u273?i\\u7875?n t\\u7883?ch v\\'f4 \\u273?\\u7883?ch thi\\'ean h\\u7841?, kh\\'f4ng bi\\u7871?t c\\'e1c ng\\u432?\\u417?i c\\'f3 mu\\u7889?n th\\u7917? hay kh\\'f4ng?\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"Ti\\'ean Duy\\'ean S\\u417?n?\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n v\\u7915?a nghe \\u273?\\'e3 th\\u7845?y quen tai, suy ngh\\u297? m\\u7897?t l\\'fac m\\u7899?i nh\\u7899? \\u273?\\u7871?n s\\u7921? t\\'ecnh n\\u7893?i b\\u7853?t m\\u7845?y th\\'e1ng nay tr\\'ean linh th\\u7889?ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch C\\u361?ng kh\\'f4ng bi\\u7871?t ai t\\u7841?o ra tr\\'e0o l\\u432?u n\\'e0y, nh\\u432?ng ngh\\u297? \\u273?\\u7871?n c\\u7843?nh nh\\u7843?y n\\'fai t\\'ecm \\u273?i\\u7875?n t\\u7883?ch c\\u361?ng th\\'edch th\\'fa kh\\'f4ng k\\'e9m.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"N\\u7871?u c\\'e1c ng\\u432?\\u417?i mu\\u7889?n \\u273?i th\\'ec c\\u7913? vi\\u7879?c, ta ch\\u7881? \\u273?i theo \\u273?\\u7875? xem n\\'e1o nhi\\u7879?t!\" T\\u7917? V\\'e2n kh\\'f4ng t\\u7915? ch\\u7889?i, thu\\u7853?n mi\\u7879?ng l\\'ean ti\\u7871?ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"\\u272?\\'fang v\\u7853?y, ta gi\\u7889?ng nh\\u432? T\\u7917? V\\'e2n, s\\u7869? kh\\'f4ng tham gia, nh\\u432?ng c\\u361?ng mu\\u7889?n xem c\\'e1c ng\\u432?\\u417?i thu ho\\u7841?ch \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c c\\'e1i g\\'ec?!\" H\\u7891? M\\u7883? Nhi g\\u7853?t \\u273?\\u7847?u ph\\u7843?n \\u7913?ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"Vi\\u7879?c n\\'e0y kh\\'f4ng kh\\'f3, m\\u7897?t l\\'e1t ta c\\u361?ng mu\\u7889?n nh\\u7843?y n\\'fai, bi\\u7871?t \\u273?\\'e2u nh\\u7863?t \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c tuy\\u7879?t th\\u7871? k\\u7923? ph\\'e1p th\\'ec sao?\" Khuy\\u7875?n D\\u7841? Xoa g\\u7853?t \\u273?\\u7847?u ph\\u7909? h\\u7885?a.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Th\\u7871? l\\'e0 Ng\\u432?u Thi\\u7871?t c\\'f9ng nh\\u7919?ng ng\\u432?\\u7901?i kh\\'e1c c\\u361?ng tham gia n\\'e1o nhi\\u7879?t, k\\u7871?t qu\\u7843? \\u273?\\u7871?n gi\\u7901? tan h\\u7885?c, c\\u7843? l\\u7899?p l\\u7853?p t\\u7913?c ch\\u7841?y xu\\u7889?ng Quang Huy Chi Th\\'e0nh.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Kh\\'f4ng n\\'f3i nhi\\u7873?u l\\u7901?i, Long B\\'e1 Thi\\'ean d\\u7851?n \\u273?\\u7847?u c\\u7843? l\\u7899?p, c\\u432?\\u7905?i m\\'e2y bay l\\'ean \\u273?\\u7881?nh n\\'fai Ti\\'ean Duy\\'ean S\\u417?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch N\\'fai n\\'e0y kh\\'f4ng cao l\\u7855?m, \\u432?\\u7899?c ch\\u7915?ng tr\\u259?m tr\\u432?\\u7907?ng, nh\\u432?ng d\\'f3c n\\'fai th\\u7859?ng \\u273?\\u7913?ng, r\\u7845?t kh\\'f3 c\\u432?\\u7899?c b\\u7897? \\u273?i l\\'ean.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \\u272?\\u7871?n n\\u417?i, b\\u7885?n h\\u7855?n \\u273?\\'e3 th\\u7845?y h\\'e0ng tr\\u259?m h\\u7885?c sinh kh\\'e1c c\\u361?ng \\u273?ang \\u273?\\u7913?ng tr\\'ean \\u273?\\u7881?nh n\\'fai ch\\u7901? t\\u7899?i l\\u432?\\u7907?t.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nghe b\\u7885?n h\\u7885? n\\'f3i v\\u7899?i nhau, c\\'e1i n\\'e0y ph\\u7843?i d\\u7921?a v\\'e0o \\u273?\\u7897? may m\\u7855?n c\\u7911?a m\\u7895?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i, v\\'ec c\\'f3 ng\\u432?\\u7901?i \\u273?\\'e3 kh\\'f4ng nh\\u7853?n \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c c\\'e1i g\\'ec.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch H\\u417?n n\\u7919?a, khi nh\\u7843?y xu\\u7889?ng c\\u361?ng kh\\'f4ng c\\u7847?n ph\\u7843?i thi tri\\u7875?n ph\\'e1p thu\\u7853?t, v\\'ec b\\'ean d\\u432?\\u7899?i \\u273?\\'e3 c\\'f3 tr\\u7853?n ph\\'e1p gi\\u7843?m t\\u7889?c.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Ch\\u7881? c\\u7847?n b\\u7885?n h\\u7855?n c\\'e1ch m\\u7863?t \\u273?\\u7845?t ch\\u7915?ng tr\\u259?m th\\u432?\\u7899?c, t\\u7889?c \\u273?\\u7897? s\\u7869? \\u273?\\u7897?t ng\\u7897?t gi\\u7843?m xu\\u7889?ng, sau \\u273?\\'f3 t\\u7915? t\\u7915? r\\u417?i xu\\u7889?ng m\\u7863?t \\u273?\\u7845?t, tuy\\u7879?t \\u273?\\u7889?i kh\\'f4ng c\\'f3 nguy hi\\u7875?m.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch B\\u7857?ng kh\\'f4ng, n\\u417?i n\\'e0y \\u273?\\'e3 s\\u7899?m b\\u7883? cao t\\u7847?ng thu th\\u7853?p, c\\u259?n b\\u7843?n kh\\'f4ng t\\u7899?i l\\u432?\\u7907?t \\u273?\\'e1m con n\\'edt choai choai nh\\u432? b\\u7885?n h\\u7855?n g\\'f3p vui.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \\u272?\\u7907?i m\\u7897?t l\\'fac th\\'ec c\\u361?ng c\\'f3 ch\\u7895? tr\\u7889?ng, Long B\\'e1 Thi\\'ean ti\\u7871?n \\u273?\\u7871?n ph\\'eda tr\\u432?\\u7899?c v\\'e1ch \\u273?\\'e1, r\\u7891?i kh\\'f4ng do d\\u7921? m\\'e0 nh\\u7843?y xu\\u7889?ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n th\\u7845?y th\\u7871?, l\\u7853?p t\\u7913?c gi\\'e0nh ch\\u7895? r\\u7891?i nh\\u7843?y theo, tuy nhi\\'ean b\\u7885?n h\\u7855?n c\\u361?ng kh\\'f4ng c\\'f3 thi tri\\u7875?n ph\\'e1p thu\\u7853?t.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Qu\\u7843? nhi\\'ean nh\\u432? l\\u7901?i \\u273?\\u7891?n, th\\u7901?i \\u273?i\\u7875?m Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n th\\u7845?y m\\'ecnh s\\u7855?p va ch\\u7841?m v\\u7899?i m\\u7863?t \\u273?\\u7845?t, t\\u7889?c \\u273?\\u7897? \\u273?\\u7897?t nhi\\'ean gi\\u7843?m m\\u7841?nh.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \\u272?\\u7871?n khi h\\u7855?n t\\'e9 xu\\u7889?ng n\\'fai, Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n m\\u7899?i l\\'f2m c\\'f2m b\\'f2 d\\u7853?y, hai m\\u7855?t l\\u7853?p t\\u7913?c ph\\'e1t s\\'e1ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch H\\u7855?n ph\\'e1t hi\\u7879?n n\\u417?i \\u273?\\'e2y c\\'f3 m\\u7897?t c\\'e1i th\\'f4ng \\u273?\\u7841?o kh\\'f4ng s\\'e2u, d\\'e0i r\\u7897?ng ch\\u7915?ng n\\u259?m th\\u432?\\u7899?c.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch M\\'e0 b\\'ean trong c\\'f3 m\\u7897?t c\\'e1i b\\'e0n \\u273?\\'e1, ph\\'eda tr\\'ean c\\'f3 m\\u7897?t quy\\u7875?n s\\'e1ch m\\'e0u h\\u7891?ng l\\'e0m h\\u7855?n h\\u432?ng ph\\u7845?n \\u273?\\u7871?n c\\u7921?c \\u273?i\\u7875?m.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch B\\'ean kia, Long B\\'e1 Thi\\'ean c\\u361?ng \\u273?\\'e3 ti\\u7871?p \\u273?\\u7845?t, sau \\u273?\\'f3 l\\'e0 Khuy\\u7875?n D\\u7841? Xoa v\\'e0 nh\\u7919?ng ng\\u432?\\u7901?i kh\\'e1c.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch H\\u7847?u nh\\u432? to\\'e0n b\\u7897? nam t\\u7917? trong l\\u7899?p \\u273?\\u7873?u tham gia, c\\'f2n \\u273?\\'e1m n\\u7919? t\\u7917? th\\'ec ch\\u7881? \\u273?\\u7913?ng coi, sau \\u273?\\'f3 \\u273?i xu\\u7889?ng xem k\\u7871?t qu\\u7843?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Trong l\\'fac m\\u7885?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i c\\'f2n \\u273?ang ph\\'e2n v\\'e2n kh\\'f4ng bi\\u7871?t n\\'ean t\\'ecm ng\\u432?\\u7901?i n\\'e0o \\u273?\\u7875? xem k\\u7871?t qu\\u7843?, th\\'ec trong \\u273?\\'e1m \\u273?\\'f4ng \\u273?\\u7897?t nhi\\'ean vang l\\'ean ti\\u7871?ng c\\u432?\\u7901?i l\\u7899?n:}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"A ha ha, kh\\'f4ng ngh\\u297? ta l\\u7841?i may m\\u7855?n nh\\u432? th\\u7871?, v\\u7915?a l\\'fac nh\\u7863?t \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c H\\'f3a Long Th\\u7847?n Ch\\u432?\\u7903?ng, \\u273?\\'fang l\\'e0 r\\u7845?t ph\\'f9 h\\u7907?p v\\u7899?i ta.\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Long B\\'e1 Thi\\'ean \\u273?\\u7897?t nhi\\'ean c\\u432?\\u7901?i l\\u7899?n l\\'e0m m\\u7885?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i ch\\'fa \\'fd, c\\'f3 kh\\'f4ng \\'edt ng\\u432?\\u7901?i c\\u361?ng v\\'ec \\u273?\\'f3 m\\'e0 ch\\u7841?y l\\u7841?i xem x\\'e9t.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nh\\'ecn quy\\u7875?n s\\'e1ch m\\'e0u v\\'e0ng tr\\'ean tay Long B\\'e1 Thi\\'ean, m\\u7885?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i l\\u7853?p t\\u7913?c hi\\u7875?u \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c nguy\\'ean nh\\'e2n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nguy\\'ean lai t\\'ean n\\'e0y nh\\u7863?t \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c m\\u7897?t quy\\u7875?n v\\u361? k\\u7929? c\\'f3 c\\u7845?p \\u273?\\u7897? kh\\'f4ng th\\u7845?p, \\u273?\\u7871?n c\\u7843? Khuy\\u7875?n D\\u7841? Xoa c\\u361?ng nh\\u432? th\\u7871?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n kh\\'f4ng ngh\\u297? Khuy\\u7875?n D\\u7841? Xoa l\\u7841?i nh\\u7863?t \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c \"T\\'e1n H\\u7891?n Thi\\u7871?t Tr\\u7843?o\", l\\'e0 v\\u361? k\\u7929? d\\'e0nh cho y\\'eau t\\u7897?c, \\u273?\\u7889?i v\\u7899?i Khuy\\u7875?n t\\u7897?c r\\u7845?t th\\'edch h\\u7907?p.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nh\\'ecn b\\u7885?n h\\u7885? nh\\u432? v\\u7853?y, Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n t\\'f2 m\\'f2 nh\\'ecn quy\\u7875?n s\\'e1ch c\\u7911?a m\\'ecnh, l\\u7853?t t\\u7899?i l\\u7853?t lui th\\'ec th\\u7845?y b\\u7889?n ch\\u7919? \"Qu\\u7923? Hoa B\\u7843?o \\u272?i\\u7875?n\".}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n}\r\n}\r\n}"
