    "content": "{\\rtf1\\ansi\\ansicpg1252\\uc1\\htmautsp\\deff2{\\fonttbl{\\f0\\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}{\\f2\\fcharset0 Georgia;}{\\f3\\fcharset0 Noto Serif;}}{\\colortbl\\red0\\green0\\blue0;\\red255\\green255\\blue255;}\\loch\\hich\\dbch\\pard\\plain\\ltrpar\\itap0{\\lang1033\\fs30\\f3\\cf0 \\cf0\\qj{\\cf1 \\cf1\\ql{{\\ltrch Ti\\u7871?p \\u273?\\'f3, h\\u7855?n th\\u7845?y c\\'f4 n\\'e0ng m\\u7903? QChat r\\u7891?i ch\\u7885?n v\\'e0o t\\'e0i kho\\u7843?n Thi\\'ean \\u272?\\u7841?o \\u272?\\u7891? Th\\u432? Qu\\'e1n, g\\u7917?i m\\'e3 s\\'e1ch l\\'ean \\u273?\\'f3 r\\u7891?i \\u273?em quy\\u7875?n s\\'e1ch c\\u7845?t v\\'e0o t\\'fai tr\\u7919? v\\u7853?t.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Sau \\u273?\\'f3 xoay ng\\u432?\\u7901?i n\\'f3i v\\u7899?i h\\u7855?n: \"S\\'e1ch \\u7903? t\\u7847?ng n\\'e0y m\\u432?\\u7907?n mi\\u7877?n ph\\'ed, nh\\u432?ng t\\u7915? t\\u7847?ng m\\u432?\\u7901?i tr\\u7903? l\\'ean ph\\u7843?i t\\u7889?n m\\u7897?t \\'edt \\u273?i\\u7875?m linh tr\\u7883?, ng\\u432?\\u417?i c\\u7913? t\\u7915? t\\u7915? m\\'e0 l\\u7921?a ch\\u7885?n.\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"Kh\\'f4ng th\\'e0nh v\\u7845?n \\u273?\\u7873?, ta \\u273?\\'e3 hi\\u7875?u quy c\\u7911? \\u7903? \\u273?\\'e2y r\\u7891?i, c\\'f3 \\u273?i\\u7873?u V\\'e2n Nhi n\\'e0y. . .\" Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n g\\u7853?t \\u273?\\u7847?u, nh\\u432?ng ch\\u7907?t nh\\u7899? t\\u7899?i chuy\\u7879?n g\\'ec \\u273?\\'f3, l\\'ean ti\\u7871?ng h\\u7887?i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"Ng\\u432?\\u417?i mu\\u7889?n h\\u7887?i c\\'e1i g\\'ec?\" T\\u7917? V\\'e2n \\u273?\\u432?a m\\u7855?t nh\\'ecn h\\u7855?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"\\'c0! N\\u7871?u nh\\u432? ta kh\\'f4ng \\u273?\\u259?ng k\\'fd m\\'e0 \\u273?em s\\'e1ch n\\'e0y r\\u7901?i kh\\u7887?i th\\u432? vi\\u7879?n, v\\u7853?y c\\'f3 chuy\\u7879?n g\\'ec kh\\'f4ng?\" Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n g\\'e3i \\u273?\\u7847?u c\\u432?\\u7901?i tr\\u7915?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nghe h\\u7855?n h\\u7887?i nh\\u432? v\\u7853?y, T\\u7917? V\\'e2n bi\\u7871?t t\\'ean n\\'e0y l\\u7841?i mu\\u7889?n l\\'e0m ra chuy\\u7879?n g\\'ec \\u273?\\'f3, n\\'e0ng kh\\u7869? l\\u7855?c \\u273?\\u7847?u r\\u7891?i n\\'f3i:}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"N\\u7871?u kh\\'f4ng \\u273?\\u259?ng k\\'fd m\\'e0 mu\\u7889?n \\u273?em s\\'e1ch ra ngo\\'e0i th\\'ec ng\\u432?\\u417?i kh\\'f4ng l\\'e0m \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c \\u273?\\'e2u, v\\'ec ng\\u432?\\u417?i c\\u259?n b\\u7843?n kh\\'f4ng th\\u7875? xuy\\'ean qua k\\u7871?t gi\\u7899?i b\\'ean ngo\\'e0i.\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"Nguy\\'ean lai l\\'e0 nh\\u432? v\\u7853?y!\" Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n nh\\u432? hi\\u7875?u ra chuy\\u7879?n g\\'ec \\u273?\\'f3, li\\'ean t\\u7909?c g\\u7853?t \\u273?\\u7847?u.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \\u272?i d\\u7841?o m\\u7897?t h\\u7891?i, Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n r\\u7911? T\\u7917? V\\'e2n l\\'ean t\\u7847?ng 46 \\u273?\\u7875? t\\'ecm m\\u7845?y th\\u7913? li\\'ean quan \\u273?\\u7871?n tu ti\\'ean gi\\u7899?i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nh\\u432?ng th\\u7901?i \\u273?i\\u7875?m h\\u7855?n v\\u7915?a b\\u432?\\u7899?c v\\'e0o \\u273?\\'e2y, tr\\'ean m\\'e0n h\\'ecnh l\\u7841?i xu\\u7845?t hi\\u7879?n th\\'f4ng b\\'e1o c\\u7911?a Thi\\'ean \\u272?\\u7841?o \\u272?\\u7891? Th\\u432? Qu\\'e1n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n t\\'f2 m\\'f2 m\\u7903? ra xem, n\\u7897?i dung b\\'ean trong l\\'e0m h\\u7855?n h\\u417?i kinh ng\\u7841?c, tuy nhi\\'ean r\\u7845?t nhanh \\u273?\\'e3 hi\\u7875?u.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Th\\'ec ra t\\u7915? t\\u7847?ng 46 tr\\u7903? l\\'ean, m\\u7897?t s\\u7889? s\\'e1ch trong \\u273?\\'e2y kh\\'f4ng \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c truy\\u7873?n cho ng\\u432?\\u7901?i ngo\\'e0i, n\\u7871?u vi ph\\u7841?m s\\u7869? b\\u7883? t\\'f4ng quy x\\u7917? l\\'fd.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n kh\\'f4ng ngh\\u297? m\\'ecnh s\\u7869? \\u273?em s\\'e1ch n\\u417?i \\u273?\\'e2y truy\\u7873?n cho ng\\u432?\\u7901?i kh\\'e1c, n\\'ean c\\'f9ng T\\u7917? V\\'e2n \\u273?i d\\u7841?o xung quanh.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Qu\\u7843? nhi\\'ean \\u273?\\'fang nh\\u432? c\\'e1i t\\'ean, tr\\'ean \\u273?\\'e2y c\\'f3 v\\'f4 v\\'e0n lo\\u7841?i s\\'e1ch m\\'e0 h\\u7855?n ch\\u432?a t\\u7915?ng nh\\'ecn th\\u7845?y qua l\\u7847?n n\\'e0o, \\u273?i\\u7873?u n\\'e0y l\\'e0m h\\u7855?n ph\\u7845?n kh\\'edch kh\\'f4ng th\\'f4i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \\u431?\\u7899?c ch\\u7915?ng m\\u7897?t ti\\u7871?ng sau, Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n ch\\u7885?n \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c b\\u7889?n quy\\u7875?n, ph\\'e2n bi\\u7879?t l\\'e0 S\\u417? L\\u432?\\u7907?t Tr\\u7853?n Ph\\'e1p, S\\u417? L\\u432?\\u7907?t Ph\\'f9 Ch\\'fa, S\\u417? L\\u432?\\u7907?t Thi\\'ean T\\'e0i \\u272?\\u7883?a B\\u7843?o, cu\\u7889?i c\\'f9ng l\\'e0 L\\u7883?ch S\\u7917? Tu Ti\\'ean Gi\\u7899?i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch H\\u7855?n l\\u7853?p t\\u7913?c m\\u7903? QChat ra \\u273?\\u259?ng k\\'fd m\\u432?\\u7907?n s\\'e1ch, c\\u7843? hai l\\u7853?p t\\u7913?c tr\\u7903? v\\u7873? chung c\\u432? \\u273?\\u7875? tu luy\\u7879?n t\\'e2m ph\\'e1p.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Trong th\\u7901?i gian k\\u7871? ti\\u7871?p, trong m\\u7897?t tu\\u7847?n \\u273?\\u7847?u ti\\'ean, gi\\'e1o vi\\'ean ch\\u7881? gi\\u7899?i thi\\u7879?u s\\u417? l\\u432?\\u7907?t v\\u7873? m\\'f4n h\\u7885?c sau \\u273?\\'f3 v\\u7873? nh\\'e0 s\\u7899?m h\\u417?n th\\u432?\\u7901?ng ng\\'e0y.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch M\\u7897?t tu\\u7847?n r\\u7845?t nhanh \\u273?\\'e3 tr\\'f4i qua, h\\'f4m nay ch\\'ednh l\\'e0 ng\\'e0y gi\\'e1o vi\\'ean ch\\'ednh th\\u7913?c gi\\u7843?ng d\\u7841?y v\\u7873? m\\'f4n h\\u7885?c c\\u7911?a m\\'ecnh.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Ng\\'e0y \\u273?\\u7847?u ti\\'ean, Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n \\u273?\\u7871?n v\\u7899?i m\\'f4n h\\u7885?c c\\u7911?a T\\'f4 ch\\u7911? nhi\\u7879?m, ch\\'ednh l\\'e0 m\\'f4n t\\'e2m ph\\'e1p.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch T\\'f4 ch\\u7911? nhi\\u7879?m \\u273?\\u7913?ng tr\\'ean b\\u7909?c gi\\u7843?ng n\\'f3i r\\u7845?t nhi\\u7873?u v\\u7873? tri th\\u7913?c tu ti\\'ean, n\\'e0o l\\'e0 linh kh\\'ed l\\'e0 g\\'ec? }\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch L\\'e0m sao \\u273?\\u7875? h\\u7845?p thu linh kh\\'ed v\\'e0o trong \\u273?an \\u273?i\\u7873?n?}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n nghe m\\u7897?t m\\u7841?ch su\\u7889?t b\\u7889?n ti\\u7871?ng, c\\u7843?m th\\u7845?y \\u273?\\u7847?u \\'f3c c\\'f3 h\\u417?i ong ong, nh\\u432?ng \\u273?\\u7891?ng th\\u7901?i c\\u361?ng h\\u7885?c \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c r\\u7845?t nhi\\u7873?u th\\u7913?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \\u272?\\u7847?u ti\\'ean l\\'e0 linh kh\\'ed kh\\'f4ng ph\\u7843?i v\\'f4 h\\u7841?n, m\\'e0 l\\'e0 c\\'f3 h\\u7841?n, d\\'f9ng r\\u7891?i s\\u7869? h\\u7871?t, mu\\u7889?n c\\'f3 ti\\u7871?p ph\\u7843?i d\\'f9ng th\\u7901?i dan d\\'e0i \\u273?\\u7875? t\\'edch tr\\u7919?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch H\\u417?n n\\u7919?a, nh\\u7919?ng ng\\u432?\\u7901?i c\\'f3 linh c\\u259?n, tu\\u7893?i th\\u7885? c\\u417? b\\u7843?n s\\u7869? l\\'e0 m\\u7897?t tr\\u259?m tu\\u7893?i, \\u273?i\\u7873?u n\\'e0y \\u273?\\'e3 \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c c\\'e1c ti\\u7873?n b\\u7889?i x\\'e1c \\u273?\\u7883?nh.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch M\\u7895?i khi \\u273?\\u7897?t ph\\'e1 m\\u7897?t ti\\u7875?u c\\u7843?nh gi\\u7899?i, ng\\u432?\\u7901?i tu ti\\'ean s\\u7869? t\\'f9y v\\'e0o c\\u7843?nh gi\\u7899?i m\\'e0 c\\'f3 th\\'eam th\\u7885? nguy\\'ean t\\u432?\\u417?ng \\u7913?ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \\u272?\\u7863?c bi\\u7879?t h\\u417?n h\\u7871?t l\\'e0 trong T\\'fay Hoa L\\'e2m C\\u7843?nh, n\\u7891?ng \\u273?\\u7897? linh kh\\'ed s\\u7869? d\\'e0y \\u273?\\u7863?c h\\u417?n b\\'ean ngo\\'e0i g\\u7845?p tr\\u259?m l\\u7847?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \\u272?\\u7875? l\\'e0m \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c \\u273?i\\u7873?u \\u273?\\'f3, c\\'e1c ti\\u7873?n b\\u7889?i \\u273?\\'e3 d\\'f9ng m\\u7891? h\\'f4i v\\'e0 n\\u432?\\u7899?c m\\u7855?t c\\u7911?a m\\'ecnh \\u273?\\u7875? \\u273?i kh\\u7855?c n\\u417?i t\\'ecm ki\\u7871?m linh m\\u7841?ch \\u273?em v\\u7873? t\\'f4ng m\\'f4n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"H\\'f4m nay ta ch\\u7881? gi\\u7843?ng d\\u7841?y \\u273?\\u7871?n \\u273?\\'e2y, c\\'e1c tri th\\u7913?c tu ti\\'ean v\\u7915?a r\\u7891?i c\\'e1c ng\\u432?\\u417?i nh\\u7845?t \\u273?\\u7883?nh ph\\u7843?i ghi nh\\u7899?, v\\'ec cu\\u7889?i n\\u259?m s\\u7869? c\\'f3 b\\'e0i thi, ai qua \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c s\\u7869? c\\'f3 th\\u432?\\u7903?ng, kh\\'f4ng qua \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c th\\'ec ph\\u7843?i \\u7903? l\\u7841?i h\\u7885?c th\\'eam m\\u7897?t n\\u259?m n\\u7919?a.\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch T\\'f4 ch\\u7911? nhi\\u7879?m n\\'f3i \\u273?\\u7871?n \\u273?\\'e2y, khu\\'f4n m\\u7863?t tr\\u7903? n\\'ean tr\\u7883?nh tr\\u7885?ng, \\u273?\\u432?a tay nh\\u7863?t quy\\u7875?n \\u272?\\u7841?i C\\u432?\\u417?ng Tu Ti\\'ean l\\'ean r\\u7891?i n\\'f3i:}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"\\u272?\\u7841?i C\\u432?\\u417?ng Tu Ti\\'ean l\\'e0 t\\'e2m \\u273?\\u7855?c c\\u7911?a c\\'e1c ti\\u7873?n b\\u7889?i \\u273?i tr\\u432?\\u7899?c vi\\u7871?t l\\u7841?i, trong \\u273?\\'e2y c\\'f3 h\\u7871?t th\\u7849?y nh\\u7919?ng \\u273?i\\u7875?m kh\\'f3 kh\\u259?n v\\'e0 c\\'e1ch kh\\u7855?c ph\\u7909?c, cho n\\'ean c\\'e1c ng\\u432?\\u417?i nh\\u7845?t \\u273?\\u7883?nh ph\\u7843?i xem qua.\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"V\\'e2ng, l\\'e3o s\\u432?!\" C\\u7843? l\\u7899?p \\u273?\\u7891?ng lo\\u7841?t h\\'f4 l\\u7899?n, sau \\u273?\\'f3 c\\u7847?m theo \\u272?\\u7841?i C\\u432?\\u417?ng Tu Ti\\'ean v\\u7873? nh\\'e0 nghi\\'ean c\\u7913?u.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tranh th\\u7911? th\\u7901?i gian \\u273?\\'f3, bu\\u7893?i s\\'e1ng h\\u7855?n s\\u7869? l\\'ean l\\u7899?p, c\\'f2n bu\\u7893?i t\\u7889?i th\\'ec tu luy\\u7879?n Ng\\u432?ng Kh\\'ed Quy\\u7871?t, m\\u7897?t m\\u7921?c l\\'e0m theo nh\\u7919?ng g\\'ec t\\'e2m ph\\'e1p h\\u432?\\u7899?ng d\\u7851?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch T\\'e2m ph\\'e1p n\\'e0y c\\'f3 \\u273?i\\u7875?m \\u273?\\u7863?c bi\\u7879?t, \\u273?\\'f3 l\\'e0 m\\u7895?i giai \\u273?o\\u7841?n \\u273?\\u7873?u \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c ghi ch\\'fa r\\'f5 r\\'e0ng, c\\u259?n b\\u7843?n kh\\'f4ng c\\'f3 ng\\u432?\\u7901?i ch\\u7881? \\u273?i\\u7875?m c\\u361?ng c\\'f3 th\\u7875? tu luy\\u7879?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch V\\u7873? ph\\u7847?n c\\'e1i g\\'ec g\\u7885?i l\\'e0 tu luy\\u7879?n, th\\'ec \\u273?\\'f3 l\\'e0 ph\\u432?\\u417?ng ph\\'e1p h\\u7845?p thu thi\\'ean \\u273?\\u7883?a linh kh\\'ed \\u7903? b\\'ean ngo\\'e0i, r\\u7891?i \\u273?\\u432?a n\\'f3 v\\'e0o trong \\u273?an \\u273?i\\u7873?n \\u273?\\u7875? c\\u7845?t gi\\u7919?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch M\\u7863?c d\\'f9 bi\\u7871?t r\\'f5 v\\u7873? t\\'e2m ph\\'e1p, nh\\u432?ng c\\'e1ch h\\'f4 h\\u7845?p n\\'e0y kh\\'e1 kh\\'f3 n\\u7855?m b\\u7855?t, c\\u259?n b\\u7843?n ph\\u7843?i luy\\u7879?n t\\u7853?p nhi\\u7873?u l\\u7847?n m\\u7899?i luy\\u7879?n th\\'e0nh.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Hu\\u7889?ng h\\u7891?, c\\'e1ch h\\'f4 h\\u7845?p n\\'e0y l\\'e0m h\\u7855?n s\\u7855?p thi\\u7871?u kh\\'f4ng kh\\'ed \\u273?\\u7875? th\\u7903?, m\\u7895?i l\\u7847?n \\u273?\\u7873?u b\\u7883? t\\u7913?c ng\\u7921?c \\u273?\\u7871?n nghi\\u7871?n r\\u259?ng nghi\\u7871?n l\\u7907?i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch H\\u7855?n kh\\'f4ng bi\\u7871?t T\\u7917? V\\'e2n th\\u7871? n\\'e0o, nh\\u432?ng th\\u7845?y ng\\u432?\\u7901?i ta l\\'e0 n\\u7919? nhi c\\'f2n kh\\'f4ng r\\'ean la m\\u7897?t ti\\u7871?ng, c\\u7899? sao h\\u7855?n ph\\u7843?i khu\\u7845?t ph\\u7909?c?}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Ngh\\u297? th\\'f4ng su\\u7889?t nh\\u432? v\\u7853?y, Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n ti\\u7871?p t\\u7909?c t\\u7853?p luy\\u7879?n, c\\u7889? g\\u7855?ng c\\u7843?m nh\\u7853?n thi\\'ean \\u273?\\u7883?a linh kh\\'ed \\u7903? xung quanh.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch H\\u7871?t th\\u7843?y m\\u7885?i chuy\\u7879?n \\u273?\\u7873?u b\\'ecnh th\\u432?\\u7901?ng, \\u273?\\u7871?n s\\'e1ng h\\'f4m sau h\\u7855?n l\\u7841?i m\\u7903? m\\u7855?t nh\\u432? bao ng\\'e0y, tuy nhi\\'ean kh\\'f4ng c\\'f3 ch\\'fat bi\\u7871?n h\\'f3a n\\'e0o.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n bi\\u7871?t \\u273?\\'e2y kh\\'f4ng ph\\u7843?i chuy\\u7879?n ng\\'e0y m\\u7897?t ng\\'e0y hai, t\\u7921? nhi\\'ean kh\\'f4ng qu\\'e1 g\\u7845?p g\\'e1p.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch C\\u7893? nh\\'e2n c\\'f3 c\\'e2u \"d\\u7909?c t\\u7889?c b\\u7845?t \\u273?\\u7841?t\", cho n\\'ean h\\u7855?n ph\\u7843?i t\\u7915? t\\u7915? m\\'e0 tu luy\\u7879?n, d\\'f9 sao th\\u7901?i gian c\\u361?ng nhi\\u7873?u n\\'ean h\\u7855?n kh\\'f4ng s\\u7907?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch V\\u7873? ph\\u7847?n h\\'f4m nay h\\u7885?c g\\'ec, th\\'ec h\\u7855?n \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c H\\u7891? l\\'e3o s\\u432? d\\u7841?y v\\u7869? ti\\'ean ph\\'f9, th\\u7913? n\\'e0y nh\\'ecn nh\\u432? \\u273?\\u417?n gi\\u7843?n, nh\\u432?ng c\\u7847?n c\\'f3 hoa tay m\\u7899?i l\\'e0m \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n v\\u7869? m\\u7897?t m\\u7841?ch \\u273?\\u7871?n h\\u7871?t gi\\u7901? c\\u361?ng ch\\u7859?ng ra c\\'e1i g\\'ec, nh\\'ecn v\\'e0o kh\\'e1c n\\'e0o \\u273?\\u7889?ng r\\'e1c.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nh\\'ecn th\\'e0nh qu\\u7843? c\\u7911?a m\\'ecnh, Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n li\\u7871?c m\\u7855?t nh\\'ecn qua T\\u7917? V\\'e2n, nguy\\'ean lai c\\'f4 n\\'e0ng kh\\'e1c bi\\u7879?t ho\\'e0n to\\'e0n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Ng\\u432?\\u7901?i ta kh\\'f4ng ch\\u7881? v\\u7869? ra h\\'ecnh d\\'e1ng c\\u7911?a ti\\'ean ph\\'f9, h\\u417?n n\\u7919?a c\\'f2n r\\u7845?t \\u273?\\u7865?p, k\\u7871?t c\\u7845?u kh\\'f4ng sai l\\u7879?ch ch\\'fat n\\'e0o.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n kh\\'f4ng kh\\u7887?i than th\\u7903?, sau \\u273?\\'f3 v\\u7873? nh\\'e0 ti\\u7871?p t\\u7909?c tu luy\\u7879?n Ng\\u432?ng Kh\\'ed Quy\\u7871?t.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch M\\u7845?y ng\\'e0y sau l\\'e0 c\\'e1c lo\\u7841?i tri th\\u7913?c v\\u7873? luy\\u7879?n \\u273?an, luy\\u7879?n kh\\'ed, c\\u361?ng nh\\u432? c\\'e1c m\\'f4n h\\u7885?c kh\\'e1c.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7843?i qua m\\u7897?t th\\u7901?i gian h\\u7885?c t\\u7853?p c\\'e1c lo\\u7841?i tri th\\u7913?c tu ti\\'ean, Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n c\\u361?ng c\\'f3 nh\\u7853?n th\\u7913?c nh\\u7845?t \\u273?\\u7883?nh.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Theo l\\'fd gi\\u7843?i c\\u7911?a h\\u7855?n, luy\\u7879?n \\u273?an v\\u7899?i luy\\u7879?n kh\\'ed ho\\'e0n to\\'e0n t\\u432?\\u417?ng \\u273?\\u7891?ng v\\u7899?i nhau, ch\\u7881? l\\'e0 kh\\'e1c \\u7903? \\u273?i\\u7875?m, luy\\u7879?n \\u273?an th\\'ec ng\\u432?ng \\u273?an l\\'e0 qu\\'e1 tr\\'ecnh quan tr\\u7885?ng nh\\u7845?t, c\\'f2n luy\\u7879?n kh\\'ed l\\'e0 giai \\u273?o\\u7841?n kh\\u7855?c linh v\\u259?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch H\\u417?n n\\u7919?a, Luy\\u7879?n \\u272?an S\\u432? c\\'f3 ch\\'edn c\\u7845?p b\\u7853?c, chia l\\'e0m nh\\u7845?t gai \\u273?\\u7871?n c\\u7917?u gai, m\\u7895?i ph\\u7849?m l\\u7841?i chia th\\'e0nh h\\u7841? ph\\u7849?m, trung ph\\u7849?m v\\'e0 th\\u432?\\u7907?ng ph\\u7849?m.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Luy\\u7879?n Kh\\'ed S\\u432? c\\u361?ng t\\u432?\\u417?ng t\\u7921? v\\u7899?i Luy\\u7879?n \\u272?an S\\u432? v\\'e0 Tr\\u7853?n Ph\\'e1p S\\u432?, \\u273?\\u7873?u c\\'f3 ch\\'edn c\\u7845?p b\\u7853?c \\u273?\\u7875? ph\\'e2n chia.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch V\\u7873? ph\\u7847?n T\\'e2m Ph\\'e1p th\\'ec ch\\u7881? c\\'f3 b\\u7889?n b\\u7853?c, t\\u7915? cao \\u273?\\u7871?n th\\u7845?p g\\u7891?m Thi\\'ean \\u272?\\u7883?a Huy\\u7873?n Ho\\'e0ng, m\\u7895?i c\\u7845?p l\\u7841?i chia th\\'e0nh nh\\u7845?t gai \\u273?\\u7871?n c\\u7917?u gai.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch T\\u7927? nh\\u432? t\\'e2m ph\\'e1p T\\'f4 ch\\u7911? nhi\\u7879?m truy\\u7873?n th\\u7909? cho h\\u7885?c sinh h\\'f4m nay l\\'e0 \\u273?\\u7883?a c\\u7845?p c\\u7917?u gai Ng\\u432?ng Kh\\'ed Quy\\u7871?t.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \\u272?\\'e2y l\\'e0 t\\'e2m ph\\'e1p trung c\\u7845?p d\\'e0nh cho \\u273?\\u7879? t\\u7917? c\\u7911?a t\\'f4ng m\\'f4n, c\\'f3 th\\u7875? luy\\u7879?n \\u273?\\u7871?n Nguy\\'ean Anh K\\u7923? m\\'e0 kh\\'f4ng g\\u7863?p tr\\u7903? ng\\u7841?i n\\'e0o.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Th\\u7901?i gian c\\u7913? tr\\'f4i, ban ng\\'e0y th\\'ec h\\u7855?n \\u273?\\u7871?n H\\u7885?c Ph\\u7911? \\u273?\\u7875? h\\u7885?c t\\u7853?p c\\'e1c lo\\u7841?i tri th\\u7913?c, ban \\u273?\\'eam th\\'ec chuy\\'ean t\\'e2m tu luy\\u7879?n Ng\\u432?ng Kh\\'ed Quy\\u7871?t.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Trong th\\u7901?i gian g\\u7847?n m\\u7897?t th\\'e1ng n\\'e0y, Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n r\\u7889?t cu\\u7897?c c\\u7843?m nh\\u7853?n \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c thi\\'ean \\u273?\\u7883?a linh kh\\'ed \\u7903? xung quanh.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \\u272?\\u7871?n cu\\u7889?i th\\'e1ng ch\\'edn, trong l\\'fac tu luy\\u7879?n, Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n c\\u7843?m th\\u7845?y to\\'e0n th\\'e2n \\u273?\\u7897?t nhi\\'ean t\\'ea d\\u7841?i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Trong kho\\u7843?nh kh\\u7855?c ng\\u7855?n ng\\u7911?i \\u273?\\'f3, d\\u432?\\u7901?ng nh\\u432? c\\'f3 m\\u7897?t lo\\u7841?i v\\u7853?t ch\\u7845?t n\\'e0o \\u273?\\'f3 \\u273?ang ch\\u7841?y trong kinh m\\u7841?ch c\\u7911?a m\\'ecnh.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Lo\\u7841?i v\\u7853?t ch\\u7845?t \\u273?\\'f3 ch\\'ednh l\\'e0 linh kh\\'ed, hi\\u7879?n t\\u7841?i h\\u7855?n \\u273?\\'e3 c\\'f3 th\\u7875? \\u273?\\u432?a linh kh\\'ed ti\\u7871?n nh\\u7853?p v\\'e0o c\\u417? th\\u7875? m\\'ecnh.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n c\\u7889? n\\'e9n kinh h\\u7927? trong l\\'f2ng, m\\u7897?t m\\u7921?c v\\u7853?n chuy\\u7875?n t\\'e2m ph\\'e1p \\u273?\\u7871?n m\\u7913?c t\\u7889?i \\u273?a.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n}\r\n}\r\n}"
