    "content": "{\\rtf1\\ansi\\ansicpg1252\\uc1\\htmautsp\\deff2{\\fonttbl{\\f0\\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}{\\f2\\fcharset0 Georgia;}{\\f3\\fcharset0 Noto Serif;}}{\\colortbl\\red0\\green0\\blue0;\\red255\\green255\\blue255;}\\loch\\hich\\dbch\\pard\\plain\\ltrpar\\itap0{\\lang1033\\fs30\\f3\\cf0 \\cf0\\qj{\\cf1 \\cf1\\ql{{\\ltrch Nghe l\\u7901?i n\\'e0y, Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n r\\u7845?t ng\\u7841?c nhi\\'ean, nh\\u432?ng ngh\\u297? l\\u7841?i, m\\'ecnh l\\'e0 thi\\u7871?u t\\'f4ng ch\\u7911? th\\'ec c\\u361?ng \\u273?o\\'e1n \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c ph\\u7847?n n\\'e0o, h\\u7859?n l\\'e0 c\\'e1ch c\\u7911?a h\\u7855?n kh\\'e1c v\\u7899?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i kh\\'e1c.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch V\\'e0 \\u273?\\'fang nh\\u432? nh\\u7919?ng g\\'ec h\\u7855?n \\u273?o\\'e1n, qu\\u7843? th\\u7853?t M\\u7879?nh H\\u7891?n \\u272?\\u259?ng c\\u7911?a h\\u7855?n s\\u7869? do ng\\u432?\\u7901?i m\\'e0 h\\u7855?n tinh t\\u432?\\u7903?ng nh\\u7845?t c\\u7845?t gi\\u7919?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u432?\\u7899?c m\\u7855?t M\\u7879?nh H\\u7891?n \\u272?\\u259?ng c\\u7911?a h\\u7855?n s\\u7869? do Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917? c\\u7845?t gi\\u7919?, ngo\\'e0i ra nh\\u7919?ng ng\\u432?\\u7901?i kh\\'e1c s\\u7869? kh\\'f4ng bi\\u7871?t v\\u7873? t\\'ecnh tr\\u7841?ng c\\u7911?a h\\u7855?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch C\\'f2n chuy\\u7879?n tu luy\\u7879?n th\\'ec h\\u7855?n c\\u7913? theo l\\'e3o s\\u432? trong H\\u7885?c Ph\\u7911? ph\\'e2n ph\\'f3 l\\'e0 \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c, m\\'e0 kh\\'f4ng th\\'edch tu luy\\u7879?n, \\u259?n r\\u7891?i ch\\u7901? ch\\u7871?t c\\u361?ng kh\\'f4ng sao, v\\'ec h\\u7855?n l\\'e0 thi\\u7871?u t\\'f4ng ch\\u7911? kia m\\'e0!}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"V\\u7873? sau ph\\u7843?i bi\\u7871?t ti\\u7871?t ch\\u7871? m\\u7897?t ch\\'fat, \\u273?\\u7915?ng c\\u7913? su\\u7889?t ng\\'e0y long nhong r\\u7891?i l\\'e0m ra m\\u7845?y tr\\'f2 ph\\'e1 l\\'e0ng ph\\'e1 x\\'f3m, ta kh\\'f4ng mu\\u7889?n c\\'e1i m\\u7863?t mo n\\'e0y b\\u7883? h\\u7911?y trong tay ng\\u432?\\u417?i \\u273?\\'e2u.\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"\\u272?\\u7891? nhi \\u273?\\'e3 r\\'f5, s\\u432? ph\\u7909? c\\u7913? vi\\u7879?c y\\'ean t\\'e2m, \\u273?\\u7891? nhi s\\u7869? kh\\'f4ng l\\'e0m ra chuy\\u7879?n ph\\'e1 l\\'e0ng ph\\'e1 x\\'f3m, \\u273?\\u7891? nhi bi\\u7871?t ph\\u7843?i l\\'e0m th\\u7871? n\\'e0o m\\u7899?i \\u273?\\'fang.\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n th\\'e0nh th\\u7853?t \\u273?\\'e1p \\u7913?ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"Hi v\\u7885?ng ng\\u432?\\u417?i l\\'e0m \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c nh\\u7919?ng g\\'ec m\\'ecnh n\\'f3i! Th\\'f4i \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c r\\u7891?i, hi\\u7879?n gi\\u7901? \\u273?\\'e3 \\u273?\\u7871?n gi\\u7901? l\\'ean l\\u7899?p, ng\\u432?\\u417?i tranh th\\u7911? \\u273?\\u7871?n H\\u7885?c Ph\\u7911? m\\u7897?t chuy\\u7871?n, nghe n\\'f3i h\\'f4m nay c\\'f3 m\\u7845?y th\\u7913? hay ho \\u273?ang ch\\u7901? \\u273?\\u7907?i ng\\u432?\\u417?i \\u273?\\u7845?y.\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917? nh\\u7865? g\\u7853?t \\u273?\\u7847?u, tuy bi\\u7871?t h\\u7855?n kh\\'f4ng k\\'ecm ch\\u7871? \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c m\\'e0 qu\\u7853?y ph\\'e1, nh\\u432?ng tin ch\\u7855?c chuy\\u7879?n t\\'e2m ph\\'e1p s\\u7869? kh\\'f4ng truy\\u7873?n lung tung ra ngo\\'e0i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch M\\u7863?c d\\'f9 nh\\'ecn h\\u7855?n c\\'e0 l\\u417? ph\\u7845?t ph\\u417?, kh\\'f4ng l\\'e0m n\\'ean tr\\'f2 tr\\u7889?ng g\\'ec, nh\\u432?ng c\\u361?ng kh\\'f4ng ph\\u7843?i k\\u7867? ng\\u7889?c, t\\u7921? nhi\\'ean bi\\u7871?t c\\'e1i g\\'ec n\\'ean n\\'f3i, c\\'e1i g\\'ec kh\\'f4ng n\\'ean.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"V\\'e2ng, s\\u432? ph\\u7909?!\" Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n \\u273?\\u7913?ng d\\u7853?y \\'f4m quy\\u7873?n thi l\\u7877?, sau \\u273?\\'f3 t\\'ecm m\\u7897?t con Ti\\'ean H\\u7841?c \\u273?\\u7875? qu\\'e1 giang.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch H\\u7885?c Ph\\u7911? h\\'f4m nay c\\u361?ng nh\\u432? m\\u7885?i ng\\'e0y, l\\u7847?n n\\'e0y do Tri\\u7871?t l\\'e3o s\\u432? d\\u7841?y thu\\u7853?t luy\\u7879?n \\u273?an.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Linh \\u273?an r\\u7845?t c\\u7847?n thi\\u7871?t cho ng\\u432?\\u7901?i tu ti\\'ean, cho n\\'ean \\'edt nh\\u7845?t c\\u361?ng ph\\u7843?i bi\\u7871?t m\\u7897?t ch\\'fat v\\u7873? thu\\u7853?t n\\'e0y.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tuy m\\'f4n h\\u7885?c luy\\u7879?n \\u273?an kh\\'f4ng y\\'eau c\\u7847?u h\\u7885?c sinh ph\\u7843?i tr\\u7903? th\\'e0nh Luy\\u7879?n \\u272?an S\\u432?, nh\\u432?ng \\'edt nh\\u7845?t c\\u361?ng ph\\u7843?i ph\\'e2n bi\\u7879?t \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c ti\\'ean d\\u432?\\u7907?c.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch V\\u7873? m\\'f4n n\\'e0y, h\\u7855?n th\\u7845?y kh\\'f4ng h\\u7907?p v\\u7899?i m\\'ecnh, n\\'ean ch\\u7881? ng\\u7891?i nghe l\\'e3o s\\u432? gi\\u7843?ng b\\'e0i, l\\'e2u l\\'e2u m\\u7899?i ch\\'fa \\'fd t\\u7899?i h\\'ecnh \\u7843?nh trong linh th\\u7889?ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch B\\u7845?t qu\\'e1 T\\u7917? V\\'e2n th\\'ec kh\\'e1c, nh\\'ecn b\\u7897? d\\u7841?ng th\\u7915?a bi\\u7871?t c\\'f4 n\\'e0ng r\\u7845?t th\\'edch m\\'f4n h\\u7885?c n\\'e0y, h\\u417?n n\\u7919?a \\u273?\\u7897? hi\\u7875?u bi\\u7871?t c\\'f2n s\\'e2u h\\u417?n nh\\u7919?ng h\\u7885?c sinh c\\'f9ng l\\u7913?a.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch M\\u7845?y ng\\'e0y sau kh\\'f4ng c\\'f3 g\\'ec kh\\'e1c bi\\u7879?t, \\u273?\\u7873?u l\\'e0 nh\\u7919?ng m\\'f4n nh\\u432?: tr\\u7853?n ph\\'e1p, kh\\'f4i l\\u7895?i, linh th\\u7921?c, ph\\'e1p quy\\u7871?t v\\'e0 nh\\u7919?ng th\\u7913? linh tinh kh\\'e1c.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch M\\u7863?c d\\'f9 H\\u7885?c Ph\\u7911? kh\\'f4ng y\\'eau c\\u7847?u h\\u7885?c sinh ph\\u7843?i h\\u7885?c t\\u7889?t t\\u7845?t c\\u7843? c\\'e1c m\\'f4n, nh\\u432?ng Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n c\\u361?ng ch\\u7885?n cho m\\'ecnh v\\'e0i m\\'f4n th\\'edch h\\u7907?p.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch H\\u417?n n\\u7919?a, h\\u7855?n c\\'f2n \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c h\\u7885?c m\\u7897?t s\\u7889? th\\u7913? k\\u7923? l\\u7841? v\\u7873? khoa h\\u7885?c, c\\'f9ng v\\u7899?i \\u273?\\'f3 l\\'e0 v\\'f4 s\\u7889? ki\\u7871?n th\\u7913?c \\u273?\\u7847?y m\\u7899?i l\\u7841?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch M\\u7845?y ng\\'e0y sau \\u273?\\'f3, vi\\u7879?c tu luy\\u7879?n t\\'e2m ph\\'e1p c\\u7911?a h\\u7855?n v\\u7851?n kh\\'f4ng c\\'f3 ti\\u7871?n tri\\u7875?n qu\\'e1 nhi\\u7873?u.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tuy nhi\\'ean v\\u7873? nh\\u7919?ng m\\u7863?t kh\\'e1c th\\'ec t\\u7889?t h\\u417?n kh\\'f4ng \\'edt, t\\u7927? nh\\u432? hi\\u7879?n t\\u7841?i h\\u7855?n \\u273?\\'e3 b\\u7853?p b\\u7865? n\\u7855?m \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c th\\'e2n ph\\'e1p V\\'f4 \\u7842?nh B\\u7897?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch C\\'f2n T\\u7917? V\\'e2n th\\'ec h\\u7855?n kh\\'f4ng bi\\u7871?t n\\'ean n\\'f3i th\\u7871? n\\'e0o m\\u7899?i ph\\u7843?i, v\\'ec ti\\u7875?u nha \\u273?\\u7847?u n\\'e0y \\u273?\\'e3 n\\u7855?m \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c Phi V\\'e2n \\u7842?nh m\\u7897?t c\\'e1ch ho\\'e0n ch\\u7881?nh.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n kh\\'f4ng bi\\u7871?t \\u273?\\'e2y l\\'e0 thi\\'ean ph\\'fa c\\u7911?a n\\'e0ng qu\\'e1 m\\u7841?nh, hay t\\u432? ch\\u7845?t l\\u297?nh ng\\u7897? c\\u7911?a m\\'ecnh qu\\'e1 k\\'e9m.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nh\\u432?ng h\\u7887?i ra m\\u7899?i bi\\u7871?t, nguy\\'ean lai l\\'e0 do thi\\'ean ph\\'fa c\\u7911?a c\\'f4 n\\'e0ng qu\\'e1 tr\\'e2u b\\'f2, h\\u7885?c g\\'ec c\\u361?ng n\\u7855?m b\\u7855?t nhanh ch\\'f3ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Bi\\u7871?t \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c chuy\\u7879?n n\\'e0y, Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n kh\\'f4ng kh\\u7887?i ng\\u7849?n \\u273?\\u7847?u nh\\'ecn l\\'ean tr\\u7901?i, c\\'f4 n\\'e0ng \\u273?\\'fang l\\'e0 bi\\u7871?t l\\'e0m ng\\u432?\\u7901?i ta \\u273?au l\\'f2ng m\\'e0.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Th\\u7845?y v\\u7867? m\\u7863?t u s\\u7847?u nh\\u432? con ma ch\\u7871?t tr\\'f4i c\\u7911?a h\\u7855?n, T\\u7917? V\\'e2n ng\\u7891?i xu\\u7889?ng b\\'ean c\\u7841?nh, th\\u7845?p gi\\u7885?ng an \\u7911?i:}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"Ng\\u432?\\u417?i kh\\'f4ng c\\u7847?n ph\\u7843?i s\\u7847?u bi nh\\u432? th\\u7871?, n\\u7871?u c\\u7889? g\\u7855?ng luy\\u7879?n t\\u7853?p, ng\\u432?\\u417?i c\\u361?ng \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c nh\\u432? ta th\\'f4i. Hu\\u7889?ng h\\u7891?, th\\'e2n ph\\'e1p c\\u7911?a ta v\\'e0 ng\\u432?\\u417?i kh\\'e1c nhau m\\u7897?t tr\\u7901?i m\\u7897?t v\\u7921?c, ng\\u432?\\u417?i kh\\'f4ng th\\u7875? \\u273?em ra so s\\'e1nh.\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"V\\'e2n Nhi, ta bi\\u7871?t ng\\u432?\\u417?i \\u273?ang an \\u7911?i ta, nh\\u432?ng ng\\u432?\\u417?i kh\\'f4ng c\\u7847?n lo l\\u7855?ng, ta ch\\u7881? c\\u7843?m kh\\'e1i v\\u7853?y th\\'f4i!\" Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n \\u273?\\u432?a tay vu\\u7889?t m\\'e1i t\\'f3c c\\u7911?a T\\u7917? V\\'e2n, th\\'e0nh th\\u7853?t tr\\u7843? l\\u7901?i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch T\\u7917? V\\'e2n th\\u7845?y h\\u7855?n \\u273?\\u432?a tay vu\\u7889?t t\\'f3c m\\'ecnh th\\'ec \\u273?\\u7883?nh ng\\u259?n c\\u7843?n, nh\\u432?ng ngh\\u297? \\u273?\\u7871?n chuy\\u7879?n g\\'ec \\u273?\\'f3 r\\u7889?t cu\\u7897?c l\\u7841?i th\\'f4i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch B\\u7845?t qu\\'e1, h\\u7855?n kh\\'f4ng th\\u7845?y tuy\\u7879?t v\\u7885?ng, v\\'ec hai t\\'ean Khuy\\u7875?n D\\u7841? Xoa v\\'e0 Ng\\u432?u Thi\\u7871?t c\\u361?ng t\\u432?\\u417?ng t\\u7921? nh\\u432? h\\u7855?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Hi\\u7879?n t\\u7841?i b\\u7885?n h\\u7885? ch\\u7881? n\\u7855?m \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c s\\u417? th\\'e0nh, c\\'f2n ch\\u432?a t\\u7899?i m\\u7913?c ti\\u7875?u th\\'e0nh, nh\\u432?ng nh\\u432? v\\u7853?y c\\u361?ng t\\u7889?t l\\u7855?m r\\u7891?i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch H\\u7891? M\\u7883? Nhi c\\'f9ng Long B\\'e1 Thi\\'ean th\\'ec ch\\u7859?ng mu\\u7889?n nh\\u7855?c t\\u7899?i, v\\'ec hai ng\\u432?\\u7901?i n\\'e0y \\u273?\\'e3 s\\u7899?m n\\u7855?m b\\u7855?t th\\'e2n ph\\'e1p t\\u7915? tr\\u432?\\u7899?c.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Ban \\u273?\\u7847?u h\\u7855?n c\\'f2n kh\\'f4ng bi\\u7871?t t\\u7841?i sao, nh\\u432?ng h\\u7887?i ra m\\u7899?i bi\\u7871?t, th\\'ec ra s\\u7889? ng\\u432?\\u7901?i h\\u7885?c tr\\u432?\\u7899?c \\u7903? nh\\'e0 c\\u361?ng kh\\'e1 nhi\\u7873?u.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch V\\'ec \\u273?\\'e2y l\\'e0 th\\'e2n ph\\'e1p \\u273?\\u7841?i tr\\'e0, h\\u7847?u nh\\u432? m\\u7895?i h\\u7885?c sinh \\u273?\\u7873?u luy\\u7879?n qua m\\u7897?t l\\u7847?n, cho n\\'ean b\\u7885?n h\\u7885? \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c cha m\\u7865? truy\\u7873?n l\\u7841?i c\\u361?ng l\\'e0 l\\u7869? th\\u432?\\u7901?ng t\\'ecnh.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch C\\'f2n hai t\\'ean Khuy\\u7875?n D\\u7841? Xoa v\\'e0 Ng\\u432?u Thi\\u7871?t th\\'ec kh\\'f4ng c\\u7847?n n\\'f3i t\\u7899?i, b\\u7885?n h\\u7885? l\\u432?\\u7901?i n\\'ean m\\u7899?i ti\\u7871?n b\\u7897? ch\\u7853?m ch\\u7841?p nh\\u432? th\\u7871?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n li\\u7871?c m\\u7855?t nh\\'ecn hai \\u273?\\u7913?a b\\u7841?n \\u273?ang luy\\u7879?n t\\u7853?p V\\'f4 \\u7842?nh B\\u7897?, trong l\\'f2ng th\\u7847?m th\\u7903? ra m\\u7897?t h\\u417?i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Ti\\u7871?p \\u273?\\'f3, h\\u7855?n l\\u7841?i b\\u432?\\u7899?c ra s\\'e2n t\\u7853?p luy\\u7879?n c\\'f9ng hai \\u273?\\u7913?a b\\u7841?n, \\u273?\\u7875? l\\u7841?i T\\u7917? V\\'e2n, H\\u7891? M\\u7883? Nhi v\\'e0 Long B\\'e1 Thi\\'ean ng\\u7891?i trong b\\'f3ng r\\'e2m h\\'f3ng chuy\\u7879?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nh\\u432?ng m\\u7899?i luy\\u7879?n \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c m\\u7897?t l\\'fac, Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n nh\\u432? ngh\\u297? t\\u7899?i chuy\\u7879?n g\\'ec \\u273?\\'f3, l\\u7853?p t\\u7913?c b\\u432?\\u7899?c v\\u7873? ph\\'eda g\\u7889?c c\\'e2y, nh\\'ecn Long B\\'e1 Thi\\'ean n\\'f3i:}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"B\\'e1 Thi\\'ean, ta bi\\u7871?t ng\\u432?\\u417?i \\u273?\\'e3 s\\u7899?m luy\\u7879?n th\\'e0nh th\\'e2n ph\\'e1p V\\'f4 \\u7842?nh B\\u7897?, h\\u417?n n\\u7919?a c\\'f2n h\\u7885?c \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c kh\\'f4ng \\'edt v\\u361? k\\u7929?, chi b\\u7857?ng ng\\u432?\\u417?i gi\\'fap ta luy\\u7879?n th\\'e2n ph\\'e1p m\\u7897?t ch\\'fat?\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n v\\u7915?a n\\'f3i v\\u7915?a c\\u7905?i \\u273?\\u7841?o ph\\u7909?c tr\\'ean ng\\u432?\\u7901?i xu\\u7889?ng, \\u273?\\u432?a cho T\\u7917? V\\'e2n gi\\u7919? gi\\'fap.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"Ha ha, chuy\\u7879?n n\\'e0y d\\u7877? n\\'f3i, ch\\'fang ta c\\u7913? \\u273?\\'e1nh nhau m\\u7897?t tr\\u7853?n l\\'e0 ng\\u432?\\u417?i \\u7855?c c\\'f3 ti\\u7871?n b\\u7897?.\" }\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Long B\\'e1 Thi\\'ean c\\u432?\\u7901?i ha h\\u7843?, v\\u7895? vai c\\u7911?a h\\u7855?n, n\\'f3i: \"B\\'e2y gi\\u7901? ta ph\\u7909? tr\\'e1ch \\u273?\\'e1nh, c\\'f2n ng\\u432?\\u417?i c\\u7913? vi\\u7879?c n\\'e9 l\\'e0 \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c.\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch L\\u7901?i c\\'f2n ch\\u432?a d\\u7913?t, Long B\\'e1 Thi\\'ean \\u273?\\'e3 \\u273?\\u7897?ng th\\u7911?, m\\u7897?t quy\\u7873?n \\u273?\\'e1nh th\\u7859?ng v\\'e0o ng\\u7921?c h\\u7855?n, tuy nhi\\'ean l\\u7921?c \\u273?\\u7841?o \\u273?\\'e3 b\\u7883? \\'e1p ch\\u7871?, v\\'ec t\\'ean n\\'e0y sinh ra \\u273?\\'e3 l\\'e0 Tr\\'edch Ti\\'ean.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch N\\u7871?u kh\\'f4ng \\'e1p ch\\u7871?, \\u273?o\\'e1n ch\\u7915?ng ch\\u7881? c\\u7847?n m\\u7897?t ng\\'f3n tay c\\u7911?a Long B\\'e1 Thi\\'ean c\\u361?ng d\\u432? s\\u7913?c \\u273?\\u432?a h\\u7855?n tr\\u7903? v\\u7873? v\\u7899?i c\\'e1t b\\u7909?i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch M\\u7855?t th\\u7845?y quy\\u7873?n c\\u432?\\u7899?c s\\u7855?p ch\\u7841?m v\\'e0o ng\\u432?\\u7901?i, Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n l\\u7853?p t\\u7913?c ph\\u7843?n \\u7913?ng, v\\u7897?i v\\'e0ng ng\\'e3 v\\u7873? sau.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch L\\u7841?i n\\'f3i, m\\u7897?t quy\\u7873?n n\\'e0y c\\u7911?a Long B\\'e1 Thi\\'ean kh\\'f4ng h\\u7873? nh\\u7865?, tuy h\\u7855?n n\\'e9 \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c ph\\u7847?n l\\u7899?n nh\\u432?ng v\\u7851?n b\\u7883? tr\\'fang m\\u7897?t ch\\'fat.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n lui v\\u7873? sau v\\'e0i b\\u432?\\u7899?c, \\u273?\\u7883?nh xoay ng\\u432?\\u7901?i ch\\u7841?y tr\\u7889?n nh\\u432?ng b\\u7883? Long B\\'e1 Thi\\'ean lao t\\u7899?i tung N\\u7897? Long C\\u432?\\u7899?c.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch M\\u7897?t c\\u432?\\u7899?c n\\'e0y nh\\'ecn c\\u7921?c k\\u7923? b\\'ecnh th\\u432?\\u7901?ng, nh\\u432?ng \\u7849?n ch\\u7913?a b\\'ean trong r\\u7845?t nhi\\u7873?u l\\u7921?c l\\u432?\\u7907?ng, l\\'e0m Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n kinh h\\'e3i kh\\'f4ng th\\'f4i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch H\\u7855?n kh\\'f4ng n\\'f3i hai l\\u7901?i, l\\u7853?p t\\u7913?c l\\'e1ch ng\\u432?\\u7901?i sang b\\'ean tr\\'e1i, nh\\u432?ng l\\u7841?i b\\u7883? Long Ng\\u7841?o Thi\\'ean \\u273?\\u432?a tay b\\u7855?t l\\u7845?y, cho \\u259?n m\\u7897?t c\\u432?\\u7899?c v\\'e0o b\\u7909?ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Th\\u7845?y h\\u7855?n b\\u7883? tr\\'fang m\\u7897?t c\\u432?\\u7899?c n\\u7863?ng nh\\u432? th\\u7871?, T\\u7917? V\\'e2n c\\'f3 h\\u417?i nh\\'edu m\\'e0y, nh\\u432?ng kh\\'f4ng c\\'f3 b\\u432?\\u7899?c ra ng\\u259?n c\\u7843?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"O\\'e0nh!\" }\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n b\\u7883? \\u273?\\'e1 l\\u259?n l\\u7897?n v\\'e0i v\\'f2ng tr\\'ean m\\u7863?t \\u273?\\u7845?t, l\\u7891?ng ng\\u7921?c nh\\u432? b\\u7883? h\\'f3p v\\'e0o, to\\'e0n b\\u7897? kh\\'f4ng kh\\'ed b\\'ean trong \\u273?\\u7873?u b\\u7883? \\u273?\\u7849?y ra ngo\\'e0i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch H\\u7855?n \\u273?\\u7883?nh m\\u7903? mi\\u7879?ng n\\'f3i \"d\\u7915?ng l\\u7841?i\", nh\\u432?ng th\\u7845?y Long B\\'e1 Thi\\'ean \\u273?\\'e3 xu\\u7845?t k\\'edch \\u273?\\'e1nh t\\u7899?i \\u273?\\'e0nh l\\'f2m c\\'f2m b\\'f2 d\\u7853?y ch\\u7841?y tr\\u7889?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \\u272?\\u7871?n chi\\u7873?u h\\'f4m \\u273?\\'f3, Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n to\\'e0n th\\'e2n b\\u7847?m d\\u7853?p, hai m\\u7855?t n\\'e2u nh\\u432? g\\u7845?u tr\\'fac, qu\\u7847?n \\'e1o l\\u7855?m lem b\\'f9n \\u273?\\u7845?t.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch K\\u7871?t qu\\u7843? l\\'e0 h\\u7855?n ph\\u7843?i \\u273?\\u7871?n Y Vi\\u7879?n ki\\u7875?m tra, may m\\'e0 kh\\'f4ng c\\'f3 \\u273?\\u7897?ng \\u273?\\u7871?n g\\'e2n c\\u7889?t, ch\\u7881? l\\'e0 v\\u7871?t th\\u432?\\u417?ng ngo\\'e0i da.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch B\\u7845?t qu\\'e1, \\u273?\\'e2y c\\u361?ng l\\'e0 l\\u7847?n \\u273?\\u7847?u h\\u7855?n \\u273?\\u7871?n Y Vi\\u7879?n, m\\u7897?t n\\u417?i h\\u7871?t s\\u7913?c l\\u7841? l\\u7851?m v\\u7873? ch\\u259?m s\\'f3c s\\u7913?c kh\\u7887?e c\\u7911?a t\\'f4ng m\\'f4n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"Ta n\\'f3i n\\'e0y B\\'e1 Thi\\'ean, ng\\u432?\\u417?i ra tay nh\\u7865? m\\u7897?t ch\\'fat kh\\'f4ng \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c \\'e0? C\\u7899? sao ph\\u7843?i \\u273?\\'e1nh v\\'e0o m\\u7863?t ta nh\\u432? th\\u7871??\" Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n nghi\\u7871?n r\\u259?ng nghi\\u7871?n l\\u7907?i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch T\\u7917? V\\'e2n v\\u7899?i H\\u7891? M\\u7883? Nhi \\u273?\\u7913?ng b\\'ean c\\u7841?nh th\\u7845?y h\\u7855?n th\\'ea th\\u7843?m nh\\u432? th\\u7871? th\\'ec che mi\\u7879?ng c\\u432?\\u7901?i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch B\\u7903?i v\\'ec nh\\'ecn h\\u7855?n l\\'fac n\\'e0y ch\\u7859?ng kh\\'e1c n\\'e0o con g\\u7845?u tr\\'fac b\\u7883? b\\u7887? \\u273?\\'f3i, v\\u7915?a \\u7889?m v\\u7915?a g\\u7847?y l\\u7841?i c\\'f2n nh\\u7887? con, nh\\'ecn ch\\u7843? ra h\\u7879? th\\u7889?ng g\\'ec.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n}\r\n}\r\n}"
