    "content": "{\\rtf1\\ansi\\ansicpg1252\\uc1\\htmautsp\\deff2{\\fonttbl{\\f0\\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}{\\f2\\fcharset0 Georgia;}{\\f3\\fcharset0 Noto Serif;}}{\\colortbl\\red0\\green0\\blue0;\\red255\\green255\\blue255;}\\loch\\hich\\dbch\\pard\\plain\\ltrpar\\itap0{\\lang1033\\fs30\\f3\\cf0 \\cf0\\qj{\\cf1 \\cf1\\ql{{\\ltrch Tho\\'e1ng c\\'e1i phi\\u7871?n l\\'e1 \\u273?\\'e3 \\u273?em h\\u7855?n n\\'e2ng l\\'ean m\\u7897?t \\u273?\\u7897? cao kh\\'f3 m\\'e0 h\\'ecnh dung, t\\u7841?i \\u273?\\'e2y kh\\'f4ng c\\'e1ch n\\'e0o nh\\'ecn th\\u7845?y v\\'f9ng bi\\u7875?n b\\'ean d\\u432?\\u7899?i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n ng\\u7849?n \\u273?\\u7847?u nh\\'ecn l\\u7841?i xung quanh, d\\u432?\\u7899?i ch\\'e2n hi\\u7879?n gi\\u7901? l\\'e0 t\\u7915?ng \\u273?o\\'e0n h\\u7855?c v\\u7909?, \\u273?\\u7847?u v\\'f2i r\\u7891?ng kia c\\u361?ng n\\u7857?m t\\'edt d\\u432?\\u7899?i ch\\'e2n h\\u7855?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917? kh\\'f4ng qu\\'e1 \\u273?\\u7875? \\'fd \\u273?\\u7871?n chuy\\u7879?n n\\'e0y, hai tay v\\u7851?n b\\u7889?i \\u7903? sau l\\u432?ng, thong dong \\u273?i\\u7873?u khi\\u7875?n phi\\u7871?n l\\'e1 bay v\\u7873? ph\\'eda \\u273?\\'f4ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch V\\u7899?i t\\u7889?c \\u273?\\u7897? phi h\\'e0nh c\\u7911?a Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917?, r\\u7845?t nhanh hai ng\\u432?\\u7901?i \\u273?\\'e3 \\u273?\\u7871?n h\\'f2n \\u273?\\u7843?o v\\'f4 danh tr\\'ean bi\\u7875?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch H\\'f2n \\u273?\\u7843?o n\\'e0y kh\\'f4ng l\\u7899?n l\\u7855?m, b\\u7889?n b\\u7873? gi\\'e1p v\\u7899?i n\\u432?\\u7899?c bi\\u7875?n m\\'eanh m\\'f4ng, quanh n\\u259?m su\\u7889?t th\\'e1ng kh\\'f4ng c\\'f3 ng\\u432?\\u7901?i t\\u7899?i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n t\\u432?\\u7903?ng m\\'ecnh \\u273?\\'e3 \\u273?\\u7871?n n\\u417?i, nh\\u432?ng khi nh\\'ecn t\\u7899?i nh\\'ecn lui, th\\u7845?y n\\u417?i \\u273?\\'e2y kh\\'f4ng c\\'f3 g\\'ec \\u273?\\u7863?c bi\\u7879?t th\\'ec c\\'f3 ch\\'fat ng\\u7849?n ng\\u432?\\u7901?i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch M\\u7863?c d\\'f9 c\\'f3 ch\\'fat nghi ho\\u7863?c trong l\\'f2ng, nh\\u432?ng h\\u7855?n kh\\'f4ng c\\'f3 l\\'ean ti\\u7871?ng tra h\\u7887?i, m\\'e0 l\\u7859?ng l\\u7863?ng theo sau s\\u432? ph\\u7909?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917? th\\u7915?a bi\\u7871?t t\\'e2m t\\u432? \\u273?\\u7891? nhi nh\\'e0 m\\'ecnh ra sao, b\\u7845?t qu\\'e1 l\\'e3o kh\\'f4ng c\\'f3 l\\'ean ti\\u7871?ng gi\\u7843?i th\\'edch.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Ch\\'ednh \\u273?i\\u7875?m \\u7845?y \\u273?\\'e3 khi\\u7871?n Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n v\\'f4 c\\'f9ng t\\'f2 m\\'f2, hai m\\u7855?t kh\\'f4ng ng\\u7915?ng ng\\'f3 tr\\u432?\\u7899?c nh\\'ecn sau.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch D\\u432?\\u7899?i s\\u7921? d\\u7851?n d\\u7855?t c\\u7911?a Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917?, hai ng\\u432?\\u7901?i \\u273?i \\u273?\\u7871?n ng\\u7885?n n\\'fai gi\\u7919?a \\u273?\\u7843?o, sau \\u273?\\'f3 chui v\\'e0o m\\u7897?t c\\'e1i hang \\u273?\\u7897?ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Hang \\u273?\\u7897?ng n\\'e0y kh\\'f4ng l\\u7899?n l\\u7855?m, cao ch\\u7915?ng hai th\\u432?\\u7899?c, nh\\u432?ng s\\'e2u bao nhi\\'eau th\\'ec kh\\'f4ng bi\\u7871?t.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n ch\\u7881? bi\\u7871?t, b\\'ean trong hang \\u273?\\u7897?ng n\\'e0y ch\\u7881? to\\'e0n m\\u7897?t m\\'e0u t\\u259?m t\\u7889?i, c\\u259?n b\\u7843?n kh\\'f4ng c\\'f3 ch\\'fat \\'e1nh s\\'e1ng n\\'e0o.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch C\\'f3 \\u273?i\\u7873?u, th\\'e2n l\\'e0 ng\\u432?\\u7901?i tu ti\\'ean, m\\u7845?y lo\\u7841?i \\u273?\\'e1 c\\'f3 th\\u7875? ph\\'e1t s\\'e1ng nh\\u432? Nguy\\u7879?t Quang Th\\u7841?ch, Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917? v\\u7889?n kh\\'f4ng thi\\u7871?u.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch V\\u7915?a ti\\u7871?n v\\'e0o, Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917? \\u273?\\'e3 th\\u7843? Nguy\\u7879?t Quang Th\\u7841?ch bay l\\u417? l\\u7917?ng tr\\'ean kh\\'f4ng trung, sau \\u273?\\'f3 t\\u7915? t\\u7915? ti\\u7871?n v\\'e0o trong.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch M\\u7897?t m\\'e0n n\\'e0y l\\'e0m Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n c\\'f3 ch\\'fat t\\'f2 m\\'f2, v\\'ec theo h\\u7855?n bi\\u7871?t, ngo\\'e0i D\\u7841? Minh Ch\\'e2u ra th\\'ec \\'edt c\\'f3 b\\u7843?o v\\u7853?t n\\'e0o c\\'f3 th\\u7875? chi\\u7871?u s\\'e1ng nh\\u432? v\\u7853?y.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nh\\u432?ng s\\u7921? t\\'ecnh h\\u7855?n kh\\'f4ng bi\\u7871?t c\\'f3 r\\u7845?t nhi\\u7873?u, n\\'ean \\u273?\\u7907?i khi n\\'e0o c\\'f3 th\\u7901?i gian, h\\u7887?i l\\u7841?i c\\u361?ng ch\\u432?a mu\\u7897?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch L\\u7841?i n\\'f3i, m\\u7863?c d\\'f9 Nguy\\u7879?t Quang Th\\u7841?ch c\\'f3 th\\u7875? chi\\u7871?u s\\'e1ng, nh\\u432?ng kh\\'f4ng gian ph\\u7911? s\\'e1ng l\\u7841?i kh\\'f4ng nhi\\u7873?u.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch B\\'ean trong th\\'f4ng \\u273?\\u7841?o v\\u7851?n t\\u7889?i \\u273?en nh\\u432? tr\\u432?\\u7899?c, ch\\u7881? l\\'e0 c\\'f3 Nguy\\u7879?t Quang Th\\u7841?ch th\\'ec an t\\'e2m h\\u417?n m\\u7897?t ch\\'fat m\\'e0 th\\'f4i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n c\\u7843?m th\\u7845?y s\\u7907? h\\'e3i n\\u417?i t\\u7889?i \\u273?en nh\\u432? n\\'e0y, n\\'ean tr\\'ean \\u273?\\u432?\\u7901?ng \\u273?i \\u273?\\u7873?u n\\u7855?m ch\\u7863?t \\u7889?ng tay \\'e1o c\\u7911?a Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Th\\u7901?i gian \\u432?\\u7899?c ch\\u7915?ng m\\u7897?t kh\\u7855?c \\u273?\\u7891?ng h\\u7891?, hai ng\\u432?\\u7901?i r\\u7889?t cu\\u7897?c \\u273?\\u7871?n \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c trung t\\'e2m c\\u7911?a ng\\u7885?n n\\'fai.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch N\\u417?i \\u273?\\'e2y v\\u7853?y m\\'e0 c\\'f3 m\\u7897?t c\\'e1i \\u273?\\u7897?ng qu\\u7853?t r\\u7897?ng l\\u7899?n, cao th\\u7845?p \\u432?\\u7899?c ch\\u7915?ng tr\\u259?m tr\\u432?\\u7907?ng, v\\'f4 c\\'f9ng r\\u7897?ng r\\'e3i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Gi\\u7901? kh\\u7855?c n\\'e0y, Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n m\\u7899?i \\u273?\\u7875? \\'fd t\\u7899?i b\\u7879? \\u273?\\'e1 r\\u7897?ng h\\u417?n m\\u432?\\u7901?i tr\\u432?\\u7907?ng \\u7903? gi\\u7919?a \\u273?\\u7897?ng qu\\u7853?t.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch H\\u7855?n bu\\'f4ng \\u7889?ng tay \\'e1o c\\u7911?a Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917?, b\\u432?\\u7899?c \\u273?\\u7871?n quan s\\'e1t b\\u7879? \\u273?\\'e1 c\\u7893?, ph\\'e1t hi\\u7879?n tr\\'ean \\u273?\\'f3 kh\\u7855?c \\u273?\\u7847?y c\\'e1c lo\\u7841?i v\\u259?n t\\u7921? th\\u7847?n b\\'ed.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch C\\u7843?nh t\\u432?\\u7907?ng n\\'e0y \\u273?\\u7875? hai m\\u7855?t Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n s\\'e1ng ng\\u7901?i, nh\\u7883?n kh\\'f4ng \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c, gi\\u7853?t gi\\u7853?t \\u7889?ng tay \\'e1o c\\u7911?a Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917?, h\\u7887?i:}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"S\\u432? ph\\u7909?, \\u273?\\'e2y l\\'e0 n\\u417?i n\\'e0o? Sao c\\'f2n ch\\u432?a th\\u7845?y t\\'f4ng m\\'f4n c\\u7911?a ch\\'fang ta?\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"Huy\\u7873?n Nhi, b\\u7879? \\u273?\\'e1 ph\\'eda tr\\u432?\\u7899?c g\\u7885?i l\\'e0 Phi Th\\u259?ng \\u272?\\'e0i, ph\\'eda tr\\'ean c\\'f3 kh\\u7855?c Phi Th\\u259?ng \\u272?\\u7841?i Tr\\u7853?n, l\\'e0 m\\u7897?t trong c\\'e1c c\\'e1ch \\u273?\\u7875? phi th\\u259?ng H\\u7891?ng M\\'f4ng \\u272?\\u7841?o Gi\\u7899?i, ti\\u7871?n v\\'e0o Quy Kh\\u432? Gi\\u7899?i.\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917? t\\u7915? t\\u7889?n gi\\u7843?i th\\'edch, \\u273?\\u7891?ng th\\u7901?i vung tay, th\\u7843? v\\'e0o \\u273?\\'f3 m\\u7897?t \\'edt th\\u432?\\u7907?ng ph\\u7849?m h\\u7891?ng m\\'f4ng th\\u7841?ch.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch H\\u7891?ng m\\'f4ng th\\u7841?ch v\\u7915?a nh\\u7853?p, ba m\\u432?\\u417?i s\\'e1u v\\u7883? tr\\'ed tr\\'ean tr\\u7853?n ph\\'e1p li\\u7873?n ph\\'e1t ra \\'e1nh s\\'e1ng m\\u7901? \\u7843?o, \\u273?em \\u273?\\u7897?ng ph\\u7911? chi\\u7871?u s\\'e1ng r\\'f5 r\\'e0ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \\u272?\\u7907?i khi b\\u7889? tr\\'ed xong m\\u7885?i th\\u7913?, Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917? m\\u7899?i quay l\\u7841?i, ch\\u7853?m r\\'e3i gi\\u7843?i th\\'edch: \"V\\u7873? ph\\u7847?n t\\'f4ng m\\'f4n c\\u7911?a ch\\'fang ta \\u7903? \\u273?\\'e2u, t\\u7921? nhi\\'ean l\\'e0 n\\u7857?m trong T\\'fay Hoa L\\'e2m C\\u7843?nh, c\\'e1ch Ph\\'e0m Gi\\u7899?i r\\u7845?t xa.\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nghe h\\u7871?t m\\u7845?y l\\u7901?i n\\'e0y, Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n c\\'f3 ch\\'fat ng\\u7849?n ng\\u432?\\u7901?i, trong l\\'f2ng n\\u7893?i l\\'ean m\\u7897?t tr\\u7853?n nghi ho\\u7863?c, kh\\'f3 tin h\\u7887?i:}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"Phi Th\\u259?ng \\u272?\\'e0i? H\\u417?n n\\u7919?a c\\'f2n n\\u7857?m trong Quy Kh\\u432? Gi\\u7899?i, T\\'fay Hoa L\\'e2m C\\u7843?nh? M\\'e0 Ph\\'e0m Gi\\u7899?i l\\'e0 n\\u417?i n\\'e0o v\\u7853?y s\\u432? ph\\u7909??\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n v\\u7889?n kh\\'f4ng hi\\u7875?u nh\\u7919?ng g\\'ec s\\u432? ph\\u7909? n\\'f3i, gi\\u7901? kh\\u7855?c n\\'e0y \\u273?\\u7893?i l\\u7841?i l\\'e0 l\\'e3o t\\u7893? nh\\'e0 h\\u7855?n, ch\\u7855?c c\\u361?ng kh\\'f4ng kh\\'e1c l\\'e0 bao.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nh\\u432?ng \\u273?i\\u7875?m n\\'e0y c\\u361?ng kh\\'f4ng th\\u7875? tr\\'e1ch h\\u7855?n, m\\u7897?t \\u273?\\u7913?a tr\\u7867? n\\u259?m tu\\u7893?i trong gia t\\u7897?c d\\u432?\\u7899?i Ph\\'e0m Gi\\u7899?i, l\\'e0m sao hi\\u7875?u \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c nh\\u7919?ng th\\u7913? n\\'e0y?}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"Ph\\'e0m Gi\\u7899?i l\\'e0 gi\\u7899?i di\\u7879?n c\\u7845?p th\\u7845?p, l\\'e0 n\\u417?i m\\'e0 ng\\u432?\\u417?i \\u273?ang sinh s\\u7889?ng, m\\u7897?t khi tu luy\\u7879?n \\u273?\\u7871?n c\\u7843?nh gi\\u7899?i nh\\u7845?t \\u273?\\u7883?nh s\\u7869? phi th\\u259?ng l\\'ean v\\u7883? di\\u7879?n cao h\\u417?n. Tr\\u432?\\u7899?c m\\u7855?t kh\\'f4ng n\\'f3i \\u273?\\u7871?n chuy\\u7879?n n\\'e0y n\\u7919?a, v\\u7873? sau ng\\u432?\\u417?i t\\u7921? nhi\\'ean s\\u7869? r\\'f5.\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917? vu\\u7889?t r\\'e2u m\\u7881?m c\\u432?\\u7901?i, m\\u7897?t tay thi tri\\u7875?n ph\\'e1p quy\\u7871?t, sau \\u273?\\'f3 d\\u7851?n Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n b\\u432?\\u7899?c v\\'e0o Phi Th\\u259?ng \\u272?\\'e0i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"B\\'e2y gi\\u7901? vi s\\u432? s\\u7869? d\\u7851?n ng\\u432?\\u417?i v\\u7873? t\\'f4ng m\\'f4n, n\\u417?i \\u273?\\'f3 c\\'f3 r\\u7845?t nhi\\u7873?u s\\u432? huynh s\\u432? mu\\u7897?i, kh\\u7881? con nh\\'e0 ng\\u432?\\u417?i tha h\\u7891? m\\'e0 ch\\u417?i \\u273?\\'f9a.\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n g\\u7853?t \\u273?\\u7847?u kh\\'f4ng n\\'f3i, trong l\\'f2ng th\\u7847?m ghi nh\\u7899?, c\\'f3 l\\u7869? \\u273?\\'e2y l\\'e0 ph\\u432?\\u417?ng ph\\'e1p gi\\'fap h\\u7855?n tr\\u7903? v\\u7873? c\\u7889? h\\u432?\\u417?ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch M\\'e0 nh\\u7919?ng ng\\u432?\\u7901?i tr\\'ean kia v\\u7889?n kh\\'f4ng bi\\u7871?t ng\\'e0y th\\'e1ng vui v\\u7867? c\\u7911?a m\\'ecnh \\u273?\\'e3 s\\u7855?p h\\u7871?t, thay v\\'e0o \\u273?\\'f3 l\\'e0 nh\\u7919?ng ng\\'e0y t\\u259?m t\\u7889?i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Ma v\\u432?\\u417?ng \\u273?\\'e3 \\u273?\\u7871?n, t\\'f4ng m\\'f4n s\\u7869? \\u273?\\'f3n l\\u7845?y nh\\u7919?ng tr\\u7853?n qu\\u7853?y ph\\'e1 t\\u432?ng b\\u7915?ng, khi\\u7871?n m\\u7885?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i kh\\'f4ng \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c ngon gi\\u7845?c \\u273?\\'e3 s\\u7855?p xu\\u7845?t th\\u7871?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Trong l\\'fac Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n \\u273?ang suy ngh\\u297? m\\'f4ng lung, tr\\u7853?n ph\\'e1p \\u273?\\'e3 v\\u7853?n chuy\\u7875?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch M\\u7845?y v\\u7841?n v\\u259?n t\\u7921? th\\u7847?n b\\'ed tr\\'ean b\\u7873? m\\u7863?t Phi Th\\u259?ng \\u272?\\'e0i \\u273?\\u7897?t nhi\\'ean ph\\'e1t ra lam quang nh\\'e0n nh\\u7841?t.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Ti\\u7871?p \\u273?\\'f3, m\\u7897?t c\\u7897?t s\\'e1ng th\\'ecnh l\\'ecnh xu\\u7845?t hi\\u7879?n, n\\'f3 \\u273?\\'e2m qua ng\\u7885?n n\\'fai, xuy\\'ean th\\u7859?ng l\\'ean b\\u7847?u tr\\u7901?i r\\u7897?ng l\\u7899?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n ng\\u417? ng\\'e1c nh\\'ecn theo, n\\u7897?i t\\'e2m kh\\'f4ng ng\\u7915?ng k\\'edch \\u273?\\u7897?ng, h\\u7853?n kh\\'f4ng th\\u7875? ph\\'f3ng t\\u7899?i \\u273?\\u7875? t\\'ecm hi\\u7875?u c\\u259?n nguy\\'ean.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \\u272?\\u7891?ng d\\u7841?ng v\\u7899?i h\\u7855?n, n\\u7871?u \\u273?\\u7875? ng\\u432?\\u7901?i kh\\'e1c nh\\'ecn th\\u7845?y m\\u7897?t m\\'e0n n\\'e0y, ch\\u7855?c ch\\u7855?n s\\u7869? gi\\u7853?t m\\'ecnh kh\\'f4ng k\\'e9m.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nh\\u432?ng m\\'e0 Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917? \\u273?\\'e3 s\\u7899?m l\\u432?\\u7901?ng tr\\u432?\\u7899?c s\\u7921? t\\'ecnh, cho n\\'ean c\\u7889? t\\'ecnh ch\\u7885?n m\\u7897?t n\\u417?i xa x\\'f4i h\\u7867?o l\\'e1nh \\u273?\\u7875? kh\\'f4ng l\\'e0m ng\\u432?\\u7901?i kh\\'e1c ch\\'fa \\'fd.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch V\\'ec v\\u7853?y, nh\\u7919?ng ng\\u432?\\u7901?i kia mu\\u7889?n th\\u7845?y c\\u361?ng kh\\'f4ng c\\'e1ch n\\'e0o th\\u7845?y \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c, b\\u7857?ng kh\\'f4ng m\\u7897?t m\\'e0n kinh t\\'e2m \\u273?\\u7897?ng ph\\'e1ch n\\'e0y s\\u7869? kh\\u7855?c s\\'e2u v\\'e0o t\\'e2m tr\\'ed h\\u7885?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"Cha, m\\u7865?, h\\'e0i nhi ph\\u7843?i \\u273?i r\\u7891?i!\" Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n \\u273?\\u432?a m\\u7855?t v\\u7873? ph\\u432?\\u417?ng xa, n\\u7897?i t\\'e2m b\\u7895?ng d\\'e2ng l\\'ean m\\u7897?t c\\u7895? chua x\\'f3t.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch C\\'f3 l\\u7869? l\\u7847?n \\u273?i n\\'e0y, r\\u7845?t l\\'e2u v\\u7873? sau m\\u7899?i \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c \\u273?o\\'e0n t\\u7909? v\\u7899?i gia \\u273?\\'ecnh, cho n\\'ean h\\u7855?n m\\u7899?i c\\'f3 t\\'e2m tr\\u7841?ng nh\\u432? th\\u7871?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nh\\u432?ng h\\u7855?n v\\u7889?n kh\\'f4ng bi\\u7871?t, Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917? l\\u7841?i l\\'e0 ng\\u432?\\u7901?i r\\'f5 r\\'e0ng h\\u417?n ai h\\u7871?t.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch M\\u7897?t khi phi th\\u259?ng H\\u7891?ng M\\'f4ng \\u272?\\u7841?o Gi\\u7899?i, ti\\u7871?n v\\'e0o Quy Kh\\u432? Gi\\u7899?i, th\\'e2n ph\\u7853?n c\\u7911?a h\\u7855?n \\u273?\\'e3 kh\\'e1c xa l\\'fac tr\\u432?\\u7899?c, kh\\'f4ng c\\'f2n l\\'e0 \\u273?\\u7913?a tr\\u7867? v\\'f4 danh ti\\u7875?u t\\u7889?t n\\u7919?a.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"Ch\\'fang ta \\u273?i th\\'f4i!\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nh\\'ecn v\\u7867? m\\u7863?t c\\u7911?a h\\u7855?n, Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917? than nh\\u7865? m\\u7897?t ti\\u7871?ng, sau \\u273?\\'f3 vung tay, m\\'e0n s\\'e1ng li\\u7873?n \\u273?\\u432?a hai ng\\u432?\\u7901?i ph\\'f3ng th\\u7859?ng l\\'ean b\\u7847?u tr\\u7901?i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"Cha, m\\u7865?, t\\u7841?m bi\\u7879?t!\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n kh\\u7869? nh\\u7855?m m\\u7855?t, sau \\u273?\\'f3 nghe ti\\u7871?ng \\u273?\\u7893? v\\u7905? vang l\\'ean, hi\\u7875?n nhi\\'ean l\\'e0 Phi Th\\u259?ng \\u272?\\'e0i \\u273?\\'e3 b\\u7883? ph\\'e1 h\\u7911?y.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nh\\u432?ng \\u273?\\u7907?i khi m\\u7903? m\\u7855?t ra, h\\u7855?n th\\u7845?y m\\'ecnh \\u273?ang di chuy\\u7875?n trong m\\u7897?t kh\\'f4ng gian v\\'f4 c\\'f9ng v\\'f4 t\\u7853?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Xung quanh ch\\u7881? to\\'e0n m\\u7897?t m\\'e0u \\u273?en t\\u259?m t\\u7889?i, nh\\u432?ng ph\\'eda xa l\\u7841?i c\\'f3 h\\u7857?ng h\\'e0 sa s\\u7889? kh\\u7889?i c\\u7847?u \\u273?ang ph\\'e1t ra \\'e1nh s\\'e1ng nh\\'e8 nh\\u7865?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch M\\u7863?c d\\'f9 kh\\'f4ng bi\\u7871?t \\u273?\\'f3 l\\'e0 g\\'ec, nh\\u432?ng n\\'f3 c\\'f3 v\\u7867? \\u273?\\u7865?p v\\'f4 c\\'f9ng h\\u7845?p d\\u7851?n, khi\\u7871?n h\\u7855?n ph\\u7843?i tr\\'f2n m\\u7855?t m\\'e0 nh\\'ecn.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"N\\u417?i \\u273?\\'e2y g\\u7885?i l\\'e0 duy \\u273?\\u7897? kh\\'f4ng gian, n\\'f3i c\\'e1ch kh\\'e1c l\\'e0 kh\\'f4ng gian r\\u7897?ng l\\u7899?n b\\'ean ngo\\'e0i v\\u361? tr\\u7909?.\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Th\\u7845?y h\\u7855?n t\\'f2 m\\'f2 nh\\u432? th\\u7871?, Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917? ng\\u7849?n \\u273?\\u7847?u nh\\'ecn v\\u7873? ph\\'eda tr\\u432?\\u7899?c, vu\\u7889?t r\\'e2u m\\u7881?m c\\u432?\\u7901?i, ch\\u7847?m ch\\u7853?m gi\\u7843?i th\\'edch:}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"V\\u7873? ph\\u7847?n m\\u7845?y qu\\u7843? c\\u7847?u kia, \\u273?\\'f3 ch\\'ednh l\\'e0 ng\\'f4i sao m\\'e0 ng\\u432?\\u417?i nh\\'ecn th\\u7845?y tr\\'ean b\\u7847?u tr\\u7901?i h\\u7857?ng \\u273?\\'eam.\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"S\\u432? ph\\u7909?, \\u273?\\'e2y. . . \\u272?\\'e2y. . . Ch\\u7859?ng l\\u7869? \\u273?\\'e2y l\\'e0 kh\\'f4ng gian ngo\\'e0i kia b\\u7847?u tr\\u7901?i?\" Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n c\\'f3 ch\\'fat l\\u7855?p b\\u7855?p, d\\u432?\\u7901?ng nh\\u432? kh\\'f4ng tin v\\'e0o nh\\u7919?ng g\\'ec m\\'ecnh th\\u7845?y.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"\\u272?\\'fang v\\u7853?y, \\u273?\\'e2y x\\'e1c th\\u7921?c l\\'e0 kh\\'f4ng gian b\\'ean ngo\\'e0i b\\u7847?u tr\\u7901?i, \\u273?\\u7891?ng th\\u7901?i c\\u361?ng l\\'e0 n\\u417?i ch\\'fang ta ph\\u7843?i \\u273?i qua \\u273?\\u7875? \\u273?\\u7871?n \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c t\\'f4ng m\\'f4n.\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917? m\\u7881?m c\\u432?\\u7901?i gi\\u7843?i th\\'edch, sau \\u273?\\'f3 ph\\'f3ng m\\u7855?t nh\\'ecn v\\u7873? ph\\u432?\\u417?ng xa, trong l\\'f2ng kh\\'f4ng bi\\u7871?t \\u273?ang ngh\\u297? \\u273?\\u7871?n chuy\\u7879?n g\\'ec.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Th\\u7845?y h\\'e0nh \\u273?\\u7897?ng c\\u7911?a s\\u432? ph\\u7909?, Tr\\u7847?n K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n \\u273?\\u432?a m\\u7855?t nh\\'ecn theo, h\\u7891?i l\\'e2u m\\u7899?i l\\'ean ti\\u7871?ng: \"S\\u432? ph\\u7909?, t\\'f4ng m\\'f4n ch\\'fang ta \\u7903? \\u273?\\'f3 sao?\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n}\r\n}\r\n}"
