    "content": "{\\rtf1\\ansi\\ansicpg1252\\uc1\\htmautsp\\deff2{\\fonttbl{\\f0\\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}{\\f2\\fcharset0 Georgia;}{\\f3\\fcharset0 Noto Serif;}}{\\colortbl\\red0\\green0\\blue0;\\red255\\green255\\blue255;}\\loch\\hich\\dbch\\pard\\plain\\ltrpar\\itap0{\\lang1033\\fs30\\f3\\cf0 \\cf0\\qj{\\cf1 \\cf1\\ql{{\\ltrch Th\\u7845?y v\\u7867? m\\u7863?t \\u273?\\u7847?y ph\\u7913?c t\\u7841?p c\\u7911?a m\\u7885?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i, Tr\\u7847?n Khi\\u7871?u Thi\\'ean kh\\u7869? h\\'edt s\\'e2u m\\u7897?t h\\u417?i, b\\u432?\\u7899?c t\\u7899?i \\'f4m quy\\u7873?n thi l\\u7877?, th\\u7853?n tr\\u7885?ng n\\'f3i:}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"N\\u7871?u \\u273?\\'e2y l\\'e0 c\\u417? duy\\'ean c\\u7911?a nhi t\\u7917?, v\\'e3n b\\u7889?i kh\\'f4ng c\\'f3 \\'fd \\u273?\\u7883?nh ng\\u259?n c\\u7843?n. Ch\\u7881? l\\'e0. . .\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch N\\'f3i \\u273?\\u7871?n \\u273?\\'e2y, Tr\\u7847?n Khi\\u7871?u Thi\\'ean b\\u7895?ng nhi\\'ean im b\\u7853?t, t\\u7921?a nh\\u432? \\u273?ang do d\\u7921? chuy\\u7879?n g\\'ec \\u273?\\'f3, th\\u7845?y v\\u7853?y Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917? li\\u7873?n d\\u7915?ng \\u273?\\u7897?ng t\\'e1c vu\\u7889?t r\\'e2u, \\u273?\\u432?a tay m\\u7881?m c\\u432?\\u7901?i n\\'f3i:}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"N\\u7871?u c\\'f3 chuy\\u7879?n mu\\u7889?n h\\u7887?i, Khi\\u7871?u Thi\\'ean gia ch\\u7911? c\\u7913? vi\\u7879?c n\\'f3i ra l\\'e0 \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c, ta s\\u7869? cho c\\'e1c ng\\u432?\\u417?i c\\'e2u tr\\u7843? l\\u7901?i th\\u7887?a \\u273?\\'e1ng.\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"Nh\\u432? v\\u7853?y. . .\" Tr\\u7847?n Khi\\u7871?u Thi\\'ean tho\\'e1ng \\u273?\\'e1nh gi\\'e1 \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c m\\u7845?t trong chuy\\u7879?n n\\'e0y, h\\u7891?i l\\'e2u m\\u7899?i l\\'ean ti\\u7871?ng, h\\u7887?i:}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"N\\u7871?u ti\\u7873?n b\\u7889?i \\u273?\\'e3 n\\'f3i nh\\u432? v\\u7853?y, v\\u7853?y cho v\\'e3n b\\u7889?i h\\u7887?i, kh\\'f4ng bi\\u7871?t khi n\\'e0o ti\\u7873?n b\\u7889?i m\\u7899?i mang ti\\u7875?u oa nhi r\\u7901?i kh\\u7887?i gia t\\u7897?c?\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch L\\u7901?i n\\'f3i v\\u7915?a ra, m\\u7885?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i l\\u7853?p t\\u7913?c n\\'edn th\\u7903?, d\\u7891?n h\\u7871?t \\'e1nh m\\u7855?t v\\u7873? ph\\'eda l\\'e3o nh\\'e2n, n\\u7897?i t\\'e2m tr\\'e0n \\u273?\\u7847?y mong \\u273?\\u7907?i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Chuy\\u7879?n n\\'e0y th\\'e0nh th\\'ec t\\u7889?t, kh\\'f4ng th\\'ec c\\u361?ng ch\\u7859?ng sao, mi\\u7877?n sao kh\\'f4ng \\u7843?nh h\\u432?\\u7903?ng \\u273?\\u7871?n s\\u7921? t\\u7891?n vong c\\u7911?a gia t\\u7897?c l\\'e0 \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c, b\\u7845?t qu\\'e1 b\\u7885?n h\\u7885? v\\u7851?n c\\'f3 m\\u7897?t ch\\'fat ch\\u7901? mong.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"Nguy\\'ean lai l\\'e0 chuy\\u7879?n n\\'e0y.\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Th\\'e2n l\\'e0 ng\\u432?\\u7901?i t\\u7915?ng tr\\u7843?i, h\\u417?n n\\u7919?a c\\'f2n s\\u7889?ng \\u273?\\u7871?n tu\\u7893?i n\\'e0y, l\\'e0m sao Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917? kh\\'f4ng bi\\u7871?t Tr\\u7847?n Khi\\u7871?u Thi\\'ean \\u273?ang ngh\\u297? g\\'ec, cho n\\'ean l\\'e3o kh\\'f4ng ch\\'fat do d\\u7921? m\\'e0 n\\'f3i:}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"V\\u7873? chuy\\u7879?n n\\'e0y th\\'ec c\\'e1c ng\\u432?\\u417?i c\\u7913? y\\'ean t\\'e2m, th\\u7853?t ra l\\'e3o phu c\\u361?ng kh\\'f4ng g\\u7845?p, cho n\\'ean c\\'e1c ng\\u432?\\u417?i c\\u7913? t\\u7915? t\\u7915? b\\u7891?i d\\u432?\\u7905?ng, \\u273?\\u7907?i khi \\u273?\\u7871?n sinh th\\u7847?n n\\u259?m tu\\u7893?i c\\u7911?a \\u273?\\u7913?a b\\'e9 n\\'e0y, ta s\\u7869? \\u273?\\'edch th\\'e2n \\u273?\\u7871?n \\u273?\\'e2y mang h\\u7855?n r\\u7901?i \\u273?i.\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Th\\'e0nh th\\u7853?t m\\'e0 n\\'f3i, tr\\u432?\\u7899?c khi \\u273?\\u432?a ra l\\u7901?i \\u273?\\u7873? ngh\\u7883? n\\'e0y, l\\'e3o \\u273?\\'e3 suy ngh\\u297? r\\u7845?t l\\'e2u, c\\u361?ng \\u273?\\'e3 s\\u7899?m \\u273?\\u432?a ra k\\u7871? ho\\u7841?ch t\\u7915? tr\\u432?\\u7899?c n\\'ean kh\\'f4ng c\\'f3 kh\\'fac m\\u7855?c trong l\\'f2ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch B\\u7845?t qu\\'e1, s\\u7903? d\\u297? Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917? \\u273?\\u432?a ra quy\\u7871?t \\u273?\\u7883?nh nh\\u432? v\\u7853?y, t\\u7921? nhi\\'ean l\\'e0 c\\'f3 nguy\\'ean nh\\'e2n c\\u7911?a n\\'f3.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Th\\u7913? nh\\u7845?t, \\u273?\\u7875? \\u273?\\u7913?a b\\'e9 \\u7903? l\\u7841?i gia t\\u7897?c n\\u259?m n\\u259?m l\\'e0 mu\\u7889?n \\u273?\\u7913?a b\\'e9 c\\'f3 cu\\u7897?c s\\u7889?ng vui v\\u7867? c\\'f9ng ng\\u432?\\u7901?i th\\'e2n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Th\\u7913? hai, l\\'e0m nh\\u432? v\\u7853?y s\\u7869? kh\\'f4ng b\\u7883? ng\\u432?\\u7901?i Tr\\u7847?n gia o\\'e1n h\\u7853?n, h\\u417?n n\\u7919?a c\\'f2n \\u273?\\u7841?t \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c s\\u7921? \\u273?\\u7891?ng t\\'ecnh r\\u7845?t l\\u7899?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Th\\u7913? ba, \\u273?\\u7913?a b\\'e9 n\\'e0y ra \\u273?\\u7901?i c\\'e1ch \\u273?\\'e2y kh\\'f4ng l\\'e2u, n\\u7871?u \\u273?em v\\u7873? t\\'f4ng m\\'f4n qu\\'e1 s\\u7899?m, v\\u7853?y tu\\u7893?i th\\u417? s\\u7869? kh\\'f4ng \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c tr\\u7885?n v\\u7865?n, h\\u417?n n\\u7919?a c\\'f2n l\\'e0m m\\u7845?t \\u273?i t\\'ecnh y\\'eau c\\u7911?a gia \\u273?\\'ecnh, n\\'ean l\\'e3o s\\u7869? kh\\'f4ng l\\'e0m ra lo\\u7841?i chuy\\u7879?n th\\u7845?t \\u273?\\u7913?c nh\\u432? th\\u7871?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch D\\u7851?u sao, th\\'e2n l\\'e0 tr\\u432?\\u7903?ng b\\u7889?i, l\\u7841?i kh\\'f4ng ph\\u7843?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i trong ma \\u273?\\u7841?o, n\\'ean Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917? kh\\'f4ng c\\'f3 \\'fd \\u273?\\u7883?nh th\\u7875? c\\u7853?y th\\u7871? hi\\u7871?p ng\\u432?\\u7901?i, v\\'ec l\\'e0m v\\u7853?y ch\\u7859?ng c\\'f3 ch\\'fat \\'fd ngh\\u297?a n\\'e0o c\\u7843?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch M\\'e0 khi nghe xong m\\u7845?y l\\u7901?i n\\'e0y, ch\\u432? v\\u7883? t\\u7897?c l\\'e3o \\u273?\\u7873?u th\\u7903? ra m\\u7897?t h\\u417?i nh\\u7865? nh\\'f5m, t\\u7921?a nh\\u432? \\u273?\\'e3 tr\\'fac \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c g\\'e1nh n\\u7863?ng trong l\\'f2ng, xem ra \\u273?\\u7889?i ph\\u432?\\u417?ng kh\\'f4ng ph\\u7843?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i kh\\'f4ng n\\'f3i l\\'fd l\\u7869?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \\u272?\\u7871?n l\\'fac n\\'e0y, m\\u7885?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i m\\u7899?i kh\\u7859?ng \\u273?\\u7883?nh suy ngh\\u297? tr\\u432?\\u7899?c kia l\\'e0 \\u273?\\'fang, l\\u7921?a ch\\u7885?n nghe theo ho\\'e0n to\\'e0n ch\\'ednh x\\'e1c.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Gi\\u7901? kh\\u7855?c n\\'e0y, t\\u7843?ng \\u273?\\'e1 \\u273?\\'e8 n\\u7863?ng trong n\\u7897?i t\\'e2m Tr\\u432?\\u417?ng Anh M\\u7841?ch c\\'f9ng nh\\u7919?ng ng\\u432?\\u7901?i kh\\'e1c \\u273?\\'e3 \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c g\\u7905? xu\\u7889?ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Hi\\u7879?n t\\u7841?i b\\u7885?n h\\u7885? r\\u7845?t ch\\u7901? mong, ch\\u7901? mong s\\u7921? t\\'ecnh l\\u7847?n n\\'e0y s\\u7869? c\\u7843?i bi\\u7871?n gia t\\u7897?c c\\u7911?a m\\'ecnh.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"\\u272?a t\\u7841? ti\\u7873?n b\\u7889?i \\u273?\\'e3 \\u432?u \\'e1i nhi t\\u7917? c\\u7911?a v\\'e3n b\\u7889?i!\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n Khi\\u7871?u Thi\\'ean vui m\\u7915?ng qu\\'e1 \\u273?\\u7895?i, l\\u7853?p t\\u7913?c \\'f4m quy\\u7873?n thi l\\u7877?, d\\'f9ng gi\\u7885?ng \\u273?i\\u7879?u tr\\u7883?nh tr\\u7885?ng, n\\'f3i:}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"B\\u7845?t qu\\'e1, nhi t\\u7917? v\\u7851?n ch\\u432?a c\\'f3 danh t\\u7921?, n\\u7871?u \\u273?\\'e3 c\\'f3 duy\\'ean s\\u432? \\u273?\\u7891? v\\u7899?i ti\\u7873?n b\\u7889?i, v\\u7853?y m\\u7901?i ti\\u7873?n b\\u7889?i \\u273?\\u7863?t cho nhi t\\u7917? c\\u7911?a v\\'e3n b\\u7889?i m\\u7897?t c\\'e1i t\\'ean.\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch M\\u7863?c d\\'f9 b\\u7843?n th\\'e2n \\u273?\\'e3 s\\u7899?m ngh\\u297? ra t\\'ean cho con trai, nh\\u432?ng v\\'ec l\\'f2ng k\\'ednh tr\\u7885?ng, Tr\\u7847?n Khi\\u7871?u Thi\\'ean m\\u7899?i \\u273?\\u432?a ra l\\u7901?i \\u273?\\u7873? ngh\\u7883? n\\'e0y.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch C\\'f9ng l\\'fac \\u273?\\'f3, Nh\\u432? Y\\'ean l\\'e3o t\\u7893? c\\u361?ng \\u273?\\u432?a m\\u7855?t nh\\'ecn sang Tr\\u7847?n Khi\\u7871?u Thi\\'ean, trong con ng\\u432?\\u417?i hi\\u7879?n ra v\\u7867? t\\'e1n \\u273?\\u7891?ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch M\\u7845?y v\\u7883? t\\u7897?c l\\'e3o nghe v\\u7853?y th\\'ec kh\\u7869? g\\u7853?t \\u273?\\u7847?u m\\u7897?t c\\'e1i, qu\\u7843? nhi\\'ean ch\\u7885?n Tr\\u7847?n Khi\\u7871?u Thi\\'ean l\\'e0m t\\u7897?c tr\\u432?\\u7903?ng l\\'e0 l\\u7921?a ch\\u7885?n ho\\'e0n to\\'e0n ch\\'ednh x\\'e1c.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch V\\u7873? ph\\u7847?n Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917?, m\\u7863?c d\\'f9 s\\u7899?m bi\\u7871?t s\\u7869? c\\'f3 chuy\\u7879?n n\\'e0y, nh\\u432?ng l\\'e3o kh\\'f4ng t\\u7915? ch\\u7889?i, m\\'e0 tr\\'e1i l\\u7841?i c\\'e0ng ho\\'e0i ni\\u7879?m.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917? b\\u432?\\u7899?c \\u273?\\u7871?n c\\u7841?nh c\\u7917?a s\\u7893?, \\u273?\\u432?a m\\u7855?t nh\\'ecn l\\'ean b\\u7847?u tr\\u7901?i, h\\u7891?i l\\'e2u sau m\\u7899?i kh\\'f4ng nhanh kh\\'f4ng ch\\u7853?m, n\\'f3i:}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"N\\u7871?u Khi\\u7871?u Thi\\'ean gia ch\\u7911? \\u273?\\'e3 \\u273?\\u7873? ngh\\u7883?, v\\u7853?y sau n\\'e0y g\\u7885?i h\\u7855?n l\\'e0 K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n \\u273?i!\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"K\\'ednh trong k\\'ednh tr\\u7885?ng, Huy\\u7873?n trong huy\\u7873?n b\\'ed, v\\u7915?a k\\'ednh tr\\u7885?ng, v\\u7915?a huy\\u7873?n b\\'ed?!\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n Khi\\u7871?u Thi\\'ean tr\\u7847?m t\\u432? ph\\'e2n t\\'edch, tuy kh\\'f4ng r\\'f5 \\'fd ngh\\u297?a s\\'e2u xa b\\'ean trong nh\\u432? th\\u7871? n\\'e0o, nh\\u432?ng h\\u7855?n v\\u7851?n cu\\u7891?ng h\\u7927?, n\\'f3i:}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"C\\'e1i t\\'ean th\\u7853?t hay, sau n\\'e0y v\\'e3n b\\u7889?i s\\u7869? g\\u7885?i nhi t\\u7917? c\\u7911?a m\\'ecnh l\\'e0 K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n.\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"Ha ha, hay cho hai ch\\u7919? K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n. \\u272?a t\\u7841? ti\\u7873?n b\\u7889?i \\u273?\\'e3 ban t\\'ean cho ti\\u7875?u ch\\u7855?c nh\\'e0 ch\\'fang ta.\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \\u272?\\u7841?i tr\\u432?\\u7903?ng l\\'e3o Tr\\u7847?n V\\'f4 B\\'e1 c\\u432?\\u7901?i l\\u7899?n, n\\u7897?i t\\'e2m qu\\'e1 \\u273?\\u7895?i h\\u432?ng ph\\u7845?n, tr\\u7921?c ti\\u7871?p l\\'ean ti\\u7871?ng \\u273?\\u7873? ngh\\u7883?:}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"V\\u7853?n T\\u7917? ti\\u7873?n b\\u7889?i, n\\u7871?u h\\'f4m nay l\\'e0 ng\\'e0y vui, v\\u7853?y h\\'e3y \\u7903? l\\u7841?i Tr\\u7847?n gia l\\'e0m kh\\'e1ch v\\'e0i h\\'f4m \\u273?i!\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"\\'c0i. . . Th\\'f4i th\\'ec t\\'f9y c\\'e1c ng\\u432?\\u417?i v\\u7853?y.\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917? th\\u7903? ra m\\u7897?t h\\u417?i, trong l\\u7901?i n\\'f3i c\\'f3 v\\'e0i ph\\u7847?n mi\\u7877?n c\\u432?\\u7905?ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tuy c\\'f3 \\'fd \\u273?\\u7883?nh t\\u7915? ch\\u7889?i, nh\\u432?ng th\\u7845?y khu\\'f4n m\\u7863?t b\\'e9 nh\\u7887? c\\u7911?a \\u273?\\u7891? t\\'f4n nh\\'e0 m\\'ecnh, l\\'e3o \\u273?\\'e0nh g\\u7853?t \\u273?\\u7847?u \\u273?\\u7891?ng \\'fd.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch D\\'f9 sao \\u7903? l\\u7841?i c\\u361?ng kh\\'f4ng c\\'f3 chuy\\u7879?n g\\'ec, hu\\u7889?ng chi ng\\u432?\\u7901?i th\\'e2n c\\u7911?a \\u273?\\u7891? nhi c\\u361?ng kh\\'f4ng qu\\'e1 an t\\'e2m v\\u7873? m\\'ecnh.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Ch\\'ednh v\\'ec v\\u7853?y, Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917? m\\u7899?i \\u273?\\u432?a ra quy\\u7871?t \\u273?\\u7883?nh \\u7903? l\\u7841?i Tr\\u7847?n gia l\\'e0m kh\\'e1ch v\\'e0i h\\'f4m.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Trong l\\'fac \\u7903? l\\u7841?i, Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917? c\\u361?ng trao \\u273?\\u7893?i m\\u7897?t s\\u7889? th\\u7913? v\\u7899?i Tr\\u7847?n gia.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nh\\u432?ng trong \\u273?\\'f3 c\\'f3 m\\u7897?t chuy\\u7879?n khi\\u7871?n m\\u7885?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i kh\\'f4ng kh\\u7887?i nghi ho\\u7863?c, \\u273?\\'f3 l\\'e0 gia t\\u7897?c kh\\'f4ng n\\'ean \\u273?\\u7863?t h\\'f4n th\\u432? cho \\u273?\\u7913?a b\\'e9 n\\'e0y.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch V\\u7873? ph\\u7847?n nguy\\'ean nh\\'e2n ra sao th\\'ec kh\\'f4ng ai bi\\u7871?t r\\'f5, v\\'ec cho d\\'f9 c\\'f3 h\\u7887?i, l\\'e3o nh\\'e2n gia Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917? ch\\u7881? tr\\u7843? l\\u7901?i m\\u7897?t c\\'e2u duy nh\\u7845?t, \\u273?\\'f3 l\\'e0 \"thi\\'ean c\\u417? b\\u7845?t kh\\u7843? l\\u7897?\".}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nghe v\\u7853?y, m\\u7885?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i c\\u361?ng kh\\'f4ng c\\'f2n g\\'ec \\u273?\\u7875? n\\'f3i, n\\u7871?u l\\'e3o nh\\'e2n gia \\u273?\\'e3 n\\'f3i nh\\u432? v\\u7853?y, v\\u7853?y th\\'ec b\\u7885?n h\\u7885? ch\\u7881? c\\u7847?n nghe theo l\\'e0 \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch M\\'e0 \\u273?\\'fang nh\\u432? d\\u7921? ki\\u7871?n, Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917? \\u7903? l\\u7841?i ba ng\\'e0y li\\u7873?n l\\u7863?ng l\\u7869? r\\u7901?i kh\\u7887?i, \\u273?\\u7875? cho ai n\\u7845?y \\u273?\\u7873?u than th\\u7903? kh\\'f4ng th\\'f4i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch C\\'f3 \\u273?i\\u7873?u, trong ba ng\\'e0y n\\'e0y, b\\u7885?n h\\u7885? ch\\u7859?ng t\\'ecm \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c th\\'f4ng tin h\\u7919?u \\'edch qu\\'e1 nhi\\u7873?u, ch\\u7881? bi\\u7871?t t\\'f4ng m\\'f4n m\\'e0 \\u273?\\u7913?a b\\'e9 s\\u7855?p \\u273?\\u7871?n c\\'f3 t\\'ean Quy Nguy\\'ean Th\\u7847?n T\\'f4ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \\u272?\\'f3 l\\'e0 t\\'f4ng m\\'f4n thu\\u7897?c phe trung l\\u7853?p, kh\\'f4ng ch\\'ednh c\\u361?ng ch\\u7859?ng t\\'e0, ngo\\'e0i \\u273?i\\u7873?u \\u273?\\'f3 ra, to\\'e0n b\\u7897? \\u273?\\u7873?u m\\u417? h\\u7891? kh\\'f3 hi\\u7875?u.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch M\\'e0 ng\\u432?\\u7901?i c\\'f3 ki\\u7871?n th\\u7913?c uy\\'ean b\\'e1c trong gia t\\u7897?c l\\'e0 Nh\\u432? Y\\'ean l\\'e3o t\\u7893?, sau khi nghe c\\'e1i t\\'ean n\\'e0y c\\u361?ng ph\\u7843?i nh\\'edu m\\'e0y nghi ho\\u7863?c.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch B\\u7903?i v\\'ec t\\u7915? l\\'fac sinh th\\u7901?i \\u273?\\u7871?n nay, n\\'e0ng ch\\u432?a nghe qua t\\'f4ng m\\'f4n n\\'e0o c\\'f3 t\\'ean Quy Nguy\\'ean Th\\u7847?n T\\'f4ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Ch\\'ed \\'edt n\\'f3 kh\\'f4ng t\\u7891?n t\\u7841?i trong Vi\\u7879?t Qu\\u7889?c, th\\u7853?m ch\\'ed l\\'e0 trong \\u273?i\\u7875?n t\\u7883?ch c\\u7893? x\\u432?a.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nh\\u432?ng suy \\u273?i ngh\\u297? l\\u7841?i v\\'e0i l\\u7847?n, n\\'e0ng kh\\u7869? g\\u7853?t \\u273?\\u7847?u, v\\'ec Huy\\u7873?n V\\u361? \\u272?\\u7841?i L\\u7909?c c\\'f3 v\\'f4 s\\u7889? t\\'f4ng m\\'f4n ti\\u7875?u ph\\'e1i, ng\\u432?\\u7901?i n\\'e0o d\\'e1m m\\u7841?nh mi\\u7879?ng n\\'f3i m\\'ecnh r\\'f5 h\\u7871?t?}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Hu\\u7889?ng h\\u7891?, tr\\u432?\\u7899?c khi \\u273?i, Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917? c\\'f2n nh\\u7845?n m\\u7841?nh l\\'e0 s\\u7869? kh\\'f4ng nh\\'fang tay v\\'e0o chuy\\u7879?n th\\u7871? t\\u7909?c.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \\u272?i\\u7873?u n\\'e0y \\u273?\\u7875? m\\u7885?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i c\\'f3 ch\\'fat th\\u7845?t v\\u7885?ng, b\\u7845?t qu\\'e1 c\\u361?ng kh\\'f4ng th\\u7875? tr\\'e1ch \\u273?\\u7889?i ph\\u432?\\u417?ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Bi\\u7871?t \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c \\u273?i\\u7873?u n\\'e0y, m\\u7885?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i ch\\u7881? c\\'f3 th\\u7875? \\u273?\\u432?a m\\u7855?t nh\\'ecn nhau, sau \\u273?\\'f3 than th\\u7903? v\\u7899?i tr\\u7901?i cao mu\\'f4n l\\u7901?i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tuy than th\\u7903? th\\'ec than th\\u7903?, nh\\u432?ng m\\u7885?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i \\u273?\\u7873?u bi\\u7871?t \\u273?o\\u7841?n duy\\'ean ph\\u7853?n n\\'e0y v\\u7851?n ch\\u432?a t\\u7853?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Mi\\u7877?n sao K\\'ednh Huy\\u7873?n c\\'f2n \\u273?\\'f3, m\\u7889?i quan h\\u7879? gi\\u7919?a hai b\\'ean v\\u7851?n s\\u7869? t\\u7891?n t\\u7841?i nh\\u432? tr\\u432?\\u7899?c.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch L\\u7841?i n\\'f3i, m\\u7863?c d\\'f9 kh\\'f4ng c\\'f3 s\\u7921? gi\\'fap \\u273?\\u7905? t\\u7915? Thi\\'ean V\\u7853?n T\\u7917?, nh\\u432?ng s\\u7921? th\\u7847?n b\\'ed c\\u7911?a ng\\u432?\\u7901?i n\\'e0y l\\'e0 th\\u7853?t, h\\u417?n n\\u7919?a c\\'f2n cao th\\'e2m kh\\'f3 l\\u432?\\u7901?ng, cho n\\'ean c\\'f3 th\\u7875? d\\'f9ng \\u273?\\u7875? h\\'f9 d\\u7885?a \\u272?\\u432?\\u7901?ng gia m\\u7897?t ch\\'fat.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Th\\'e2n l\\'e0 t\\u7917? \\u273?\\u7883?ch v\\u7899?i nhau, Tr\\u7847?n Khi\\u7871?u Thi\\'ean kh\\'f4ng tin \\u272?\\u432?\\u7901?ng gia s\\u7869? \\u273?\\u7875? y\\'ean khi bi\\u7871?t t\\'f4ng m\\'f4n c\\u7911?a con trai kh\\'f4ng nh\\'fang tay v\\'e0o chuy\\u7879?n th\\u7871? t\\u7909?c.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch C\\u361?ng may l\\'e0 Tr\\u7847?n gia kh\\'f4ng c\\'f3 ngo\\u7841?i nh\\'e2n, c\\u7897?ng th\\'eam t\\u7897?c nh\\'e2n h\\u7871?t m\\u7921?c che ch\\u7903? n\\'ean m\\u7885?i chuy\\u7879?n r\\u7845?t nhanh \\u273?\\'e3 l\\u7855?ng xu\\u7889?ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch V\\u7899?i l\\u7841?i Tr\\u7847?n Khi\\u7871?u Thi\\'ean c\\u361?ng kh\\'f4ng ph\\u7843?i k\\u7867? ngu, n\\'ean h\\u7855?n li\\u7873?n \\'e2m th\\'e2m cho ng\\u432?\\u7901?i lan truy\\u7873?n ra ngo\\'e0i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch C\\'f3 \\u273?i\\u7873?u h\\u7855?n s\\u7869? n\\'f3i lo\\'e1ng tho\\'e1ng v\\u7873? t\\'f4ng m\\'f4n, h\\u417?n n\\u7919?a c\\'f2n th\\u7893?i ph\\u7891?ng l\\'ean v\\'f4 s\\u7889? l\\u7847?n, \\u273?\\u7875? cho \\u272?\\u432?\\u7901?ng gia s\\u7907? n\\'e9m chu\\u7897?t v\\u7905? b\\'ecnh.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n}\r\n}\r\n}"
