    "content": "{\\rtf1\\ansi\\ansicpg1252\\uc1\\htmautsp\\deff2{\\fonttbl{\\f0\\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}{\\f2\\fcharset0 Georgia;}{\\f3\\fcharset0 Noto Serif;}}{\\colortbl\\red0\\green0\\blue0;\\red255\\green255\\blue255;}\\loch\\hich\\dbch\\pard\\plain\\ltrpar\\itap0{\\lang1033\\fs30\\f3\\cf0 \\cf0\\qj{\\cf1 \\cf1\\ql{{\\ltrch Tr\\u259?m v\\u7841?n n\\u259?m v\\u7873? tr\\u432?\\u7899?c, th\\u7901?i \\u273?i\\u7875?m \\u273?\\u7841?i ki\\u7871?p gi\\'e1ng xu\\u7889?ng Ti\\u7875?u Nguy\\'ean Tinh, huy\\u7873?n kh\\'ed b\\u7855?t \\u273?\\u7847?u kh\\'f4i ph\\u7909?c.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Huy\\u7873?n kh\\'ed kh\\'f4i ph\\u7909?c, kh\\'f4ng nh\\u7919?ng l\\'e0m c\\'e2y c\\u7889?i sinh tr\\u432?\\u7903?ng nhanh h\\u417?n, m\\'e0 ngay c\\u7843? hung th\\'fa c\\u361?ng sinh ra bi\\u7871?n d\\u7883?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Hung th\\'fa bi\\u7871?n d\\u7883?, linh tr\\'ed khai m\\u7903?, tr\\'ed tu\\u7879? kh\\'f4ng h\\u7873? thua k\\'e9m nh\\'e2n lo\\u7841?i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nh\\'e2n lo\\u7841?i c\\u361?ng kh\\'f4ng ngo\\u7841?i l\\u7879?, tr\\u432?\\u7899?c kia s\\u7889?ng \\u273?\\u7871?n s\\'e1u m\\u432?\\u417?i tu\\u7893?i xem nh\\u432? tr\\u432?\\u7901?ng th\\u7885? hi\\u7871?m th\\u7845?y.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nh\\u432?ng b\\'e2y gi\\u7901?, s\\u7889?ng \\u273?\\u7871?n s\\'e1u m\\u432?\\u417?i tu\\u7893?i m\\'e0 kh\\'f4ng c\\u7847?n ph\\u7909?c d\\u7909?ng b\\u7845?t k\\u7923? \\u273?an d\\u432?\\u7907?c n\\'e0o.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \\u7902? th\\u7901?i \\u273?\\u7841?i n\\'e0y, ph\\'e0m nh\\'e2n b\\u7855?t \\u273?\\u7847?u t\\'ecm hi\\u7875?u m\\u7897?t \\'edt \\u273?i\\u7875?n t\\u7883?ch c\\u7893? x\\u432?a, th\\'f4ng qua \\u273?\\'f3, t\\u7915? t\\u7915? b\\u432?\\u7899?c l\\'ean con \\u273?\\u432?\\u7901?ng tu luy\\u7879?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Con \\u273?\\u432?\\u7901?ng tu luy\\u7879?n n\\'e0y l\\u7845?y v\\'f5 nh\\u7853?p \\u273?\\u7841?o, v\\'f5 \\u273?\\u7841?o vi t\\'f4n, \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c ng\\u432?\\u7901?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i x\\u432?ng t\\u7909?ng l\\'e0 huy\\u7873?n v\\u361? gi\\u7843?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Ch\\u7881? b\\u7845?t qu\\'e1, kh\\'f4ng ph\\u7843?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i n\\'e0o c\\u361?ng c\\'f3 th\\u7875? tr\\u7903? th\\'e0nh huy\\u7873?n v\\u361? gi\\u7843?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch V\\'ec mu\\u7889?n tr\\u7903? th\\'e0nh huy\\u7873?n v\\u361? gi\\u7843?, b\\u7843?n th\\'e2n ph\\u7843?i c\\'f3 c\\'e1i g\\u7885?i l\\'e0 huy\\u7873?n m\\u7841?ch.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch C\\'f3 huy\\u7873?n m\\u7841?ch, b\\u7843?n th\\'e2n m\\u7899?i c\\u7843?m nh\\u7853?n \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c thi\\'ean \\u273?\\u7883?a huy\\u7873?n kh\\'ed, m\\u7899?i c\\u7843?m nh\\u7853?n \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c s\\u7913?c m\\u7841?nh bao la c\\u7911?a tr\\u7901?i \\u273?\\u7845?t.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Ch\\'ednh v\\'ec ph\\u7843?i h\\u7845?p thu thi\\'ean \\u273?\\u7883?a huy\\u7873?n kh\\'ed \\u273?\\u7875? tu luy\\u7879?n, n\\'ean n\\u417?i \\u273?\\'e2y \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c g\\u7885?i l\\'e0 huy\\u7873?n v\\u361? gi\\u7899?i, ngh\\u297?a l\\'e0 th\\u7871? gi\\u7899?i c\\u7911?a ng\\u432?\\u7901?i luy\\u7879?n v\\'f5.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch V\\u7873? ph\\u7847?n nh\\u7919?ng ng\\u432?\\u7901?i tu luy\\u7879?n n\\u7897?i c\\'f4ng, \\u273?i theo con \\u273?\\u432?\\u7901?ng l\\u7847?n m\\'f2n c\\u361?ng \\u273?\\'e3 b\\u7887? cu\\u7897?c.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch V\\'ec tu luy\\u7879?n huy\\u7873?n kh\\'ed c\\'f3 qu\\'e1 nhi\\u7873?u th\\u7871? m\\u7841?nh m\\'e0 ng\\u432?\\u7901?i tu luy\\u7879?n n\\u7897?i c\\'f4ng kh\\'f4ng c\\'e1ch n\\'e0o s\\'e1nh b\\u7857?ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nh\\u7853?t nguy\\u7879?t thoi \\u273?\\u432?a, tho\\'e1ng c\\'e1i kh\\'f4ng bi\\u7871?t \\u273?\\'e3 tr\\'f4i qua bao nhi\\'eau v\\u7841?n n\\u259?m.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Trong m\\u7845?y v\\u7841?n n\\u259?m n\\'e0y, Ti\\u7875?u Nguy\\'ean Tinh \\u273?\\'e3 tr\\u7843?i qua hai l\\u7847?n ti\\u7875?u ki\\u7871?p, khi\\u7871?n huy\\u7873?n v\\u361? gi\\u7899?i c\\'e0ng l\\'fac c\\'e0ng l\\u7909?i b\\u7841?i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch M\\u7845?y tr\\u259?m n\\u259?m sau, Huy\\u7873?n V\\u361? \\u272?\\u7841?i L\\u7909?c, Vi\\u7879?t Qu\\u7889?c, An Ch\\'e2u, Huy\\u7879?n Lam \\u272?i\\u7873?n, b\\'ean c\\u7841?nh Thanh Phong Tr\\u7845?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Thanh Phong Tr\\u7845?n l\\'e0 m\\u7897?t trong hai m\\u432?\\u417?i b\\u7889?n tr\\u7845?n c\\u7911?a Huy\\u7879?n Lam \\u272?i\\u7873?n, \\u273?\\u7883?a h\\'ecnh ch\\u7911? y\\u7871?u l\\'e0 \\u273?\\u7891?i n\\'fai, nh\\'e2n kh\\u7849?u th\\u7853?p ph\\u7847?n th\\u432?a th\\u7899?t.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch B\\'ean c\\u7841?nh Thanh Phong Tr\\u7845?n c\\'f3 m\\u7897?t h\\'f2n \\u273?\\u7843?o n\\u7857?m \\u273?\\u7897?c l\\u7853?p gi\\u7919?a c\\'e1i h\\u7891? c\\u7921?c l\\u7899?n, n\\u432?\\u7899?c h\\u7891? quanh n\\u259?m xanh bi\\u7871?t, \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c m\\u7885?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i g\\u7885?i v\\u7899?i c\\'e1i t\\'ean Thanh Phong \\u272?\\u7843?o.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Trung t\\'e2m \\u273?\\u7843?o l\\'e0 ng\\u7885?n n\\'fai cao h\\u417?n ng\\'e0n tr\\u432?\\u7907?ng, d\\'f3c n\\'fai th\\u7859?ng \\u273?\\u7913?ng, ng\\u432?\\u7901?i th\\u432?\\u7901?ng c\\u259?n b\\u7843?n kh\\'f4ng th\\u7875? leo l\\'ean, \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c g\\u7885?i l\\'e0 Thanh Phong S\\u417?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tuy n\\'f3i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i th\\u432?\\u7901?ng kh\\'f4ng th\\u7875? leo l\\'ean, nh\\u432?ng tr\\'ean \\u273?\\u7881?nh n\\'fai l\\u7841?i c\\'f3 m\\u7897?t t\\'f2a ki\\u7871?n tr\\'fac chi\\u7871?m di\\u7879?n t\\'edch c\\u7921?c l\\u7899?n, \\u273?\\'ecnh \\u273?\\'e0i l\\u7847?u c\\'e1c c\\u361?ng theo \\u273?\\'f3 m\\'e0 m\\u7885?c l\\'ean kh\\u7855?p n\\u417?i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch S\\u7889?ng tr\\'ean \\u273?\\'f3 l\\'e0 Tr\\u7847?n gia, m\\u7897?t trong nh\\u7919?ng huy\\u7873?n v\\u361? th\\u7871? gia c\\u7911?a Huy\\u7879?n Lam \\u272?i\\u7873?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch M\\'e0 l\\'fac n\\'e0y \\u273?\\'e3 l\\'e0 \\u273?\\'eam khuya v\\u7855?ng l\\u7863?ng, tr\\u259?ng tr\\'f2n treo l\\u417? l\\u7917?ng tr\\'ean cao, \\u273?\\u7875? kh\\'f4ng gian b\\'ean d\\u432?\\u7899?i \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c chi\\u7871?u s\\'e1ng r\\'f5 r\\'e0ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch T\\u7841?i tr\\u7841?ch vi\\u7879?n d\\'e0nh cho gia ch\\u7911?, Tr\\u7847?n Khi\\u7871?u Thi\\'ean \\u273?\\u7913?ng ng\\u7891?i kh\\'f4ng y\\'ean, c\\u7913? ng\\u7891?i m\\u7897?t l\\'fac l\\u7841?i \\u273?\\u7913?ng d\\u7853?y \\u273?i t\\u7899?i \\u273?i lui.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Th\\'f4ng qua \\u273?\\'e2y c\\'f3 th\\u7875? th\\u7845?y \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c s\\u7921? lo l\\u7855?ng c\\u7911?a Tr\\u7847?n Khi\\u7871?u Thi\\'ean, v\\'ec v\\u7853?y l\\'fac n\\'e0o y c\\u361?ng nh\\'ecn ch\\u7857?m ch\\u7857?m v\\'e0o c\\u259?n ph\\'f2ng \\u273?ang \\u273?\\'f3ng c\\u7917?a.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Sau l\\u432?ng Tr\\u7847?n Khi\\u7871?u Thi\\'ean l\\'e0 c\\'e1i b\\'e0n \\u273?\\'e1, ng\\u7891?i t\\u7841?i \\u273?\\'f3 l\\'e0 b\\u7889?n v\\u7883? t\\u7897?c l\\'e3o c\\'f9ng m\\u7897?t v\\u7883? n\\u7919? t\\u7917? xinh \\u273?\\u7865?p.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch N\\u259?m ng\\u432?\\u7901?i b\\u7885?n h\\u7885? l\\'e0 n\\u259?m c\\'e2y tr\\u7909? ch\\u7889?ng tr\\u7901?i c\\u7911?a Tr\\u7847?n gia, \\u273?\\u7891?ng th\\u7901?i l\\'e0 nh\\u7919?ng ng\\u432?\\u7901?i c\\'f3 quy\\u7873?n l\\u7921?c nh\\u7845?t.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Ri\\'eang n\\u7919? t\\u7917? nh\\'ecn c\\'f3 v\\u7867? tr\\u7867? trung kia, c\\'e0ng l\\'e0m cho ng\\u432?\\u7901?i ta c\\'f3 c\\u7843?m gi\\'e1c v\\'f4 c\\'f9ng th\\u7847?n b\\'ed.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tuy n\\'e0ng kh\\'f4ng c\\'f3 g\\'ec n\\u7893?i b\\u7853?t, nh\\u432?ng khu\\'f4n m\\u7863?t l\\u7841?i ng\\u259?n b\\u7903?i kh\\u259?n l\\u7909?a, khi\\u7871?n ng\\u432?\\u7901?i ta kh\\'f4ng c\\'e1ch n\\'e0o nh\\'ecn th\\u7845?u.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Hu\\u7889?ng h\\u7891?, b\\u7889?n v\\u7883? l\\'e3o \\u273?\\u7847?u kia c\\'f2n \\u273?\\u7889?i v\\u7899?i n\\'e0ng v\\'f4 c\\'f9ng th\\u7853?n tr\\u7885?ng, ch\\u7913?ng t\\u7887? th\\'e2n ph\\u7853?n trong gia t\\u7897?c kh\\'f4ng h\\u7873? th\\u7845?p k\\'e9m.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Gi\\u7901? kh\\u7855?c n\\'e0y, \\u273?\\u7875? ng\\u432?\\u7901?i kh\\'e1c nh\\'ecn th\\u7845?y ch\\u7855?c ch\\u7855?n s\\u7869? gi\\u7853?t m\\'ecnh, b\\u7903?i v\\'ec n\\u7919? t\\u7917? kia ch\\'ednh l\\'e0 \\u273?\\u7883?nh h\\u7843?i th\\u7847?n tr\\'e2m c\\u7911?a Tr\\u7847?n gia, Tr\\u7847?n Nh\\u432? Y\\'ean.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch B\\'ecnh th\\u432?\\u7901?ng n\\'e0ng kh\\'f4ng bao gi\\u7901? r\\u7901?i kh\\u7887?i T\\u7883?ch Y\\'ean C\\u432?, tuy nhi\\'ean h\\'f4m nay l\\'e0 ng\\'e0y tr\\u7885?ng \\u273?\\u7841?i, v\\'ec v\\u7853?y n\\'e0ng m\\u7899?i xu\\u7845?t hi\\u7879?n \\u7903? ch\\u7895? n\\'e0y.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Hi\\u7879?n t\\u7841?i n\\'e0ng \\u273?ang ng\\u7891?i u\\u7889?ng tr\\'e0 c\\'f9ng m\\u7845?y v\\u7883? t\\u7897?c l\\'e3o, m\\u7897?t b\\'ean quan s\\'e1t \\u273?\\u7897?ng t\\u297?nh trong ph\\'f2ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tuy n\\'f3i b\\u7873? ngo\\'e0i b\\u7885?n h\\u7885? kh\\'f4ng c\\'f3 bi\\u7875?u hi\\u7879?n g\\'ec l\\'e0 \\u273?ang lo l\\u7855?ng, nh\\u432?ng n\\u7897?i t\\'e2m ai n\\u7845?y \\u273?\\u7873?u phi\\u7873?n mu\\u7897?n kh\\'f4ng th\\'f4i.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch D\\'f9 sao t\\u7927? l\\u7879? sinh con b\\u7883? m\\u7845?t m\\u7841?ng t\\u7841?i huy\\u7873?n v\\u361? gi\\u7899?i l\\'e0 \\u273?i\\u7873?u kh\\'f4ng hi\\u7871?m, trong th\\u7871? gi\\u7899?i n\\'e0y, h\\u7857?ng ng\\'e0y c\\'f3 kh\\'f4ng bi\\u7871?t bao nhi\\'eau s\\u7921? t\\'ecnh t\\u432?\\u417?ng t\\u7921?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Cho n\\'ean gia ch\\u7911? Tr\\u7847?n Khi\\u7871?u Thi\\'ean m\\u7899?i c\\'f3 bi\\u7875?u hi\\u7879?n \\u273?\\u7913?ng ng\\u7891?i kh\\'f4ng y\\'ean, nh\\u432? ng\\u7891?i tr\\'ean \\u273?\\u7889?ng l\\u7917?a.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch C\\'f3 \\u273?i\\u7873?u, th\\'e2n l\\'e0 tr\\u432?\\u7903?ng b\\u7889?i trong nh\\'e0, n\\u259?m ng\\u432?\\u7901?i b\\u7885?n h\\u7885? \\u273?\\'e3 s\\u7899?m ch\\u7913?ng ki\\u7871?n kh\\'f4ng bi\\u7871?t bao nhi\\'eau s\\u7921? t\\'ecnh t\\u432?\\u417?ng t\\u7921?, cho n\\'ean \\u273?\\'e3 s\\u7899?m c\\'f3 ph\\'f2ng b\\u7883?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Th\\'e0nh th\\u7853?t m\\'e0 n\\'f3i, tuy r\\u7857?ng \\u273?\\'e3 c\\'f3 chu\\u7849?n b\\u7883? t\\u7915? tr\\u432?\\u7899?c, nh\\u432?ng trong l\\'f2ng m\\u7885?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i v\\u7851?n kh\\'f4ng tr\\'e1nh kh\\u7887?i s\\u7921? th\\u7845?p th\\u7887?m.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch B\\u7845?t qu\\'e1, b\\u7885?n h\\u7885? kh\\'f4ng c\\'f3 bi\\u7875?u hi\\u7879?n ra ngo\\'e0i, d\\'f9 sao th\\'e2n l\\'e0 tr\\u432?\\u7903?ng b\\u7889?i, t\\u7921? nhi\\'ean ph\\u7843?i c\\'f3 s\\u7921? chu\\u7849?n m\\u7921?c.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \\u272?\\'e1m gia t\\u432?\\u7899?ng \\u273?\\u7913?ng canh g\\'e1c b\\'ean ngo\\'e0i c\\u361?ng h\\u7891?i h\\u7907?p kh\\'f4ng k\\'e9m, th\\u7853?m ch\\'ed c\\'f3 th\\u7875? n\\'f3i l\\'e0 kh\\'f4ng thua k\\'e9m g\\'ec gia ch\\u7911?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch S\\u7903? d\\u297? n\\'f3i gia t\\u432?\\u7899?ng kh\\'f4ng thua k\\'e9m g\\'ec gia ch\\u7911? l\\'e0 v\\'ec m\\u7885?i chuy\\u7879?n thu\\u7853?n l\\u7907?i, b\\u7885?n h\\u7855?n s\\u7869? \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c ban th\\u432?\\u7903?ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch V\\u7873? ph\\u7847?n ng\\u432?\\u7907?c l\\u7841?i, t\\u7921? nhi\\'ean l\\'e0 kh\\'f4ng \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c c\\'e1i g\\'ec, th\\u7853?m ch\\'ed c\\'f2n ch\\u7913?ng ki\\u7871?n gia t\\u7897?c l\\'e2m v\\'e0o nguy c\\u417?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \\u272?\\'e2y l\\'e0 chuy\\u7879?n \\u273?\\'e1m gia t\\u432?\\u7899?ng c\\'f9ng t\\u7897?c nh\\'e2n kh\\'f4ng mu\\u7889?n th\\u7845?y nh\\u7845?t.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch D\\'f9 sao, th\\'e2n l\\'e0 ng\\u432?\\u7901?i trong t\\u7897?c, ai l\\u7841?i mu\\u7889?n chuy\\u7879?n \\u273?au bu\\u7891?n x\\u7843?y ra c\\u417? ch\\u7913??}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch R\\u417?i v\\'e0o t\\'ecnh c\\u7843?nh \\u273?\\'f3, kh\\'f4ng ch\\u7881? gia ch\\u7911? \\u273?au l\\'f2ng, m\\'e0 gia t\\u7897?c l\\u7841?i c\\'f3 chuy\\u7879?n kh\\'f4ng vui, m\\u7885?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i t\\u7921? nhi\\'ean c\\u361?ng kh\\'f4ng vui theo.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch V\\'ec v\\u7853?y b\\u7885?n h\\u7855?n m\\u7899?i kh\\u7849?n c\\u7847?u v\\u7899?i t\\u7893? ti\\'ean, kh\\u7849?n c\\u7847?u v\\u7899?i tr\\u7901?i cao, mong cho phu nh\\'e2n \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c m\\u7865? tr\\'f2n con vu\\'f4ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Trong l\\'fac m\\u7885?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i \\u273?ang tr\\u7847?m t\\u432? lo l\\u7855?ng, t\\u7913? tr\\u432?\\u7903?ng l\\'e3o Tr\\u7847?n V\\'f4 Ho\\'e0nh l\\u7863?ng l\\u7869? l\\u7845?y trong ng\\u432?\\u7901?i ra m\\u7897?t quy\\u7875?n \\u272?\\u7849?u Vi Tinh S\\u7889?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Ch\\u7881? th\\u7845?y ng\\u432?\\u7901?i n\\'e0y \\u273?\\u7863?t quy\\u7875?n s\\'e1ch l\\'ean b\\'e0n, sau \\u273?\\'f3 l\\u7845?y trong tay \\'e1o ra m\\u7897?t c\\'e1i \\u7889?ng tre, hai tay n\\u7855?m ch\\u7863?t r\\u7891?i x\\u7889?c l\\'ean.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"X\\u7891?ng x\\u7897?c. . . x\\u7891?ng x\\u7897?c. . .\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \\'c2m thanh qu\\u7867? tre va ch\\u7841?m vang l\\'ean, Tr\\u7847?n Khi\\u7871?u Thi\\'ean c\\'f9ng nh\\u7919?ng ng\\u432?\\u7901?i kh\\'e1c \\u273?\\u7891?ng lo\\u7841?t \\u273?\\u432?a m\\u7855?t nh\\'ecn theo.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nh\\u432? Y\\'ean l\\'e3o t\\u7893? nghe v\\u7853?y th\\'ec nh\\'edu m\\'e0y, c\\'f3 \\u273?i\\u7873?u n\\'e0ng kh\\'f4ng c\\'f3 l\\'ean ti\\u7871?ng ng\\u259?n c\\u7843?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tuy \\'edt khi r\\u7901?i kh\\u7887?i T\\u7883?ch Y\\'ean C\\u432?, nh\\u432?ng t\\u7915?ng nghe qua l\\u7901?i \\u273?\\u7891?n th\\u7893?i v\\u7873? t\\u7913? tr\\u432?\\u7903?ng l\\'e3o Tr\\u7847?n V\\'f4 Ho\\'e0nh, n\\'ean n\\'e0ng mu\\u7889?n nh\\'ecn th\\u7917? m\\u7897?t ch\\'fat.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch D\\u432?\\u7899?i s\\u7921? ch\\u259?m ch\\'fa c\\u7911?a to\\'e0n th\\u7875? m\\u7885?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i, \\u7889?ng tre \\u273?\\u7897?t nhi\\'ean r\\u417?i ra n\\u259?m qu\\u7867?, khi\\u7871?n ai n\\u7845?y \\u273?\\u7873?u cau m\\'e0y nghi ho\\u7863?c.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nh\\u7883? tr\\u432?\\u7903?ng l\\'e3o Tr\\u7847?n V\\'f4 Qu\\'e2n th\\u7845?y v\\u7853?y, hai m\\u7855?t ch\\u7907?t nheo l\\u7841?i, \\u273?\\u7863?t chung tr\\'e0 xu\\u7889?ng, lo l\\u7855?ng h\\u7887?i:}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"T\\u7913? \\u273?\\u7879?, qu\\u7867? t\\u432?\\u7907?ng n\\'e0y th\\u7871? n\\'e0o? L\\'e0 t\\u7889?t hay x\\u7845?u? L\\'e0 b\\'ecnh an hay nguy an? L\\'e0 h\\u7927? s\\u7921? hay tang s\\u7921??\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"T\\u7913? th\\'fac, qu\\u7867? n\\'e0y. . . Qu\\u7867? n\\'e0y cho k\\u7871?t qu\\u7843? th\\u7871? n\\'e0o?\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n Khi\\u7871?u Thi\\'ean c\\u7921?c k\\u7923? h\\u7891?i h\\u7907?p, hai tay kh\\'f4ng ng\\u7915?ng si\\u7871?t ch\\u7863?t v\\'e0o nhau, gi\\u7885?ng \\u273?i\\u7879?u c\\'f3 ch\\'fat run r\\u7849?y.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Nh\\u7919?ng ng\\u432?\\u7901?i c\\'f2n l\\u7841?i c\\u361?ng kh\\'f4ng kh\\'e1c l\\'e0 m\\u7845?y, to\\'e0n b\\u7897? \\u273?\\u7873?u d\\u7891?n m\\u7855?t v\\u7873? ph\\'eda t\\u7913? tr\\u432?\\u7903?ng l\\'e3o Tr\\u7847?n V\\'f4 Ho\\'e0nh v\\u7899?i c\\'e1i nh\\'ecn \\u273?\\u7847?y ch\\u7901? mong.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \\u7902? trong gia t\\u7897?c, ai kh\\'f4ng bi\\u7871?t \\u273?\\u7871?n t\\'e0i b\\'f3i to\\'e1n c\\u7911?a t\\u7913? tr\\u432?\\u7903?ng l\\'e3o Tr\\u7847?n V\\'f4 Ho\\'e0nh?}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch C\\u417? h\\u7891?, ng\\u432?\\u7901?i n\\'e0y b\\'f3i ra c\\'e1i g\\'ec th\\'ec \\u273?i\\u7873?u \\u273?\\'f3 s\\u7869? th\\'e0nh s\\u7921? th\\u7853?t, v\\'ec v\\u7853?y m\\u7885?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i m\\u7899?i lo l\\u7855?ng nh\\u432? th\\u7871?.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\'e1i ng\\u432?\\u7907?c v\\u7899?i v\\u7867? ch\\u7901? mong c\\u7911?a m\\u7885?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i, t\\u7913? tr\\u432?\\u7903?ng l\\'e3o Tr\\u7847?n V\\'f4 Ho\\'e0nh c\\u7913? nh\\'ecn ch\\u7857?m ch\\u7857?m v\\'e0o qu\\u7867? t\\u432?\\u7907?ng, th\\u7853?t l\\'e2u c\\u361?ng kh\\'f4ng l\\'ean ti\\u7871?ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Ph\\'e1t hi\\u7879?n c\\'f3 \\u273?i\\u7875?m b\\u7845?t th\\u432?\\u7901?ng, m\\u7885?i ng\\u432?\\u7901?i nh\\u7883?n kh\\'f4ng \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c m\\'e0 r\\'f9ng m\\'ecnh m\\u7897?t c\\'e1i, c\\u7843?m gi\\'e1c kh\\'f3 th\\u7903? l\\u7853?p t\\u7913?c tr\\'e0n ng\\u7853?p kh\\u7855?p tr\\u7841?ch vi\\u7879?n.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"T\\u7913? th\\'fac, qu\\u7867? n\\'e0y. . . Qu\\u7867? n\\'e0y l\\'e0m sao v\\u7853?y?\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n Khi\\u7871?u Thi\\'ean t\\u7921?a nh\\u432? \\u273?\\u7913?ng tr\\'ean \\u273?\\u7889?ng l\\u7917?a, c\\u7921?c k\\u7923? mu\\u7889?n bi\\u7871?t \\u273?\\'e1p \\'e1n t\\u7915? mi\\u7879?ng \\u273?\\u7889?i ph\\u432?\\u417?ng.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"Qu\\u7867? n\\'e0y. . .\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch T\\u7913? tr\\u432?\\u7903?ng l\\'e3o Tr\\u7847?n V\\'f4 Ho\\'e0nh h\\'edt s\\'e2u m\\u7897?t h\\u417?i, c\\u7889? n\\'e9n run r\\u7849?y, li\\u7871?c m\\u7855?t nh\\'ecn v\\u7873? ph\\'eda Tr\\u7847?n Khi\\u7871?u Thi\\'ean, th\\u7845?p gi\\u7885?ng n\\'f3i:}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"Ng\\u432?\\u7901?i s\\u7889?ng s\\u7907? nh\\u7845?t ba d\\'e0i hai ng\\u7855?n, ng\\u432?\\u7901?i ch\\u7871?t s\\u7907? nh\\u7845?t ba ng\\u7855?n m\\u7897?t d\\'e0i, \\u273?\\'e2y l\\'e0 qu\\u7867? hung, h\\u417?n n\\u7919?a c\\'f2n c\\u7921?c hung l\\'e0 \\u273?\\u7857?ng kh\\'e1c.\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch \"C\\'e1i. . . C\\'e1i g\\'ec? \\u272?\\'e2y l\\'e0 qu\\u7867? hung? H\\u417?n n\\u7919?a c\\'f2n c\\u7921?c hung?\"}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n{{\\ltrch Tr\\u7847?n Khi\\u7871?u Thi\\'ean kh\\'f4ng ng\\u7915?ng run r\\u7849?y, gi\\u7885?ng n\\'f3i v\\'f4 c\\'f9ng k\\'edch \\u273?\\u7897?ng, h\\u7853?n kh\\'f4ng th\\u7875? g\\'e0o l\\u7899?n \\u273?\\u7875? x\\'e1c nh\\u7853?n l\\u7841?i l\\u7847?n n\\u7919?a.}\\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n}\r\n}\r\n}"
